ocKodE_qMH-4dpj0WGqdJX7UClvjncz8sa6y35p8-HJiDBvzrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both Dentists in this practice are great. Extremely gentle. The office is well managed and the staff well trained","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Agnes Oleander","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0zFzwB1xW24lIbps2aKz-HGxW4gilv9N6f75voFr7164WYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A wonderful first experience! Looking forward to future visits at such an understanding dental clinic :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Onur Cobanoglu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfvggTDNMCRYY0rZiYeSV0beaNIUw3sInE9-_Kl63wVlnVow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ellen was amazing as always, lucky to have her as our dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shea Owens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbrpJLwgF53quK-53_Oa3-HLdDtYFNMPjjlN9fQNZu-ixCc0Ps=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First visit with Dr. Carter was very pleasant. It’s a small practice so I got more time with him than I have in the past at other places, where the assistants would clean my teeth and I’d only see the dentist for a moment. He was very friendly and knowledgeable and answered all my questions. He didn’t recommend any invasive procedures that I didn’t need. He’s conservative with what he recommends for his patients and I appreciate that, since I’ve had dentists in the past who recommended all kinds of things that weren’t necessary. The office isn’t fancy, but I’ll take a more personal, friendly visit with low cost over that any day!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2RcEBmFZiLY-p-Zsyr74IZ3OcFMpR66QkzxRyZBI_G6avABPqENtBWS-L0ANf1W2Q41F9CQvykCqGZo5bmzdx2P1A_NYIPdbbVt18zVcDaHRyx2dwD4SCgXmRImrErxAfyA3KnoA=k-no"],"When":"2019-8-2"},{"Name":"W Barr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnGq2Yh7u1r1pzThBTgkhgzzjtyq2eZQH1gxWWhybvh9o-DP79lA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My teeth-cleaning experience yesterday with Dr. Vargas was entirely positive – no complaints.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CeCe Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHds_EiQb6vQ7INHB8UXCUiJRrU_Q8CIpAZfqrkPgHLn2csQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dentistry office makes going to the dentist stress free. The office staff is very friendly and knowledgeable, even helping sort out insurance issues. The dentists here are kind, personable and concerned about patients welfare. I’ve hesitated to go to the dentist for years. I’m so thankful I found Seattle Dentists.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jean Meirink","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5fnMrRUEeeSXgMH6LKzeJ0s_Bosi2w-f5WJ3zmBTRqI3GXg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This office is great.  I had a tooth emergency and they were able to consult with me that day and fix it 2 days later. Very gentle and professional in the entire office.  I'm going to make this my go-to dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ling Xu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiwgLRvWkplVn1Y38vP84liDyHV1eSmbCROLEvVHOvwS5qfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my family are all under care of Dr Carter. I want spread the word for him so more people can benefit from his skill. Dr Carter and his staff are very friendly, we feel welcomed every time of our visit. Also, the most important, he charges a very reasonable fee for all patients, we never feel ripped off after visiting his office. I Will recommend him to all people who has dental need.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
