d":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"children","name":"Children","options":[{"name":"Nursing room","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"James Chavez Gaytan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKKD0SpekMGdwYdtXTokN1edfNmEykZUXDP7EPmWdv5m47Xg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you, Dr. V, for making my implant appointment go so smoothly! The dental hygienist, Carrie, did a great job getting me numb, and Jane did a wonderful job assisting and making me feel comfortable.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3H3iZfk-3s2TC-dot0Mtd8R-cD2k3zF7iZj38xvo-ONnGdyLDeF5u5FgpOQg0dqzA8nh9WPjqT4FbV23NPgnCD86z_5a32tCgogHoxTxkjp5WHz7tUEXkL1A-GU772BnLn_q46JlAviC4=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-24"},{"Name":"Ricky Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTLOBlAqCyqAivsYtDTtG7fAjxy8duSEnVyDroVbMZ4qSV2A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. The doctors and assistants are wonderful. I saw Dr. V for a root canal and a crown. Two separate visits, the first she was assisted by Mariana and today by Liz. They work so well together and explain everything and continue to ask if I’m ok throughout the visit. If you are looking for doctors and hygienists who care, this is the place. I have worked in dental for the 8 years so I know good providers when I meet them! Dr V, Marina, Liz I am so grateful for your time. 🥰","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Molly Hubbard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqNsl2dr51kxQLNGAX1or9opP1aipCvwyiibLIXR4mgnAHhi0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a new patient and it was a very smooth and easy process. I called to schedule an appointment. The woman on the phone collected my insurance information and booked me within the next month or so. My new patient appointment was 2 hours, the first hour spent on cleaning and then the second when I actually met my dentist for their assessment. The hygienist was amazing and super personable making sure I was comfortable and stopping whenever stinging pain arose. I am looking forward to coming back in a month for my next cleaning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dawnell stirkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRuLOZWWpnYydD7pXUkFcVl-056uJLGPGOTvSA1BbrAChYaw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fastest filling replacement repair ever!! After the numbness kicked in, it was 20 minutes. Start to finish to repair and  no pain!\nsuper cool people I love Dr. Alice.!! Thank you","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pam Becker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrqzBT0MvdgsyXySuiQx4MP7itTPXvisG99mMp0UXJnDrW5i9Z3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone here was very nice and kind. I have some anxiety and had been avoiding going to the dentist for a few years, but no one made me feel bad and in fact, other than having my teeth cleaned, I did not need any more work done! Dr. V,  Mariana, James, and China were all very gentle.  I recommend them highly!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hallie Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdLWA11euKcbKLtQ0eUOLdKF07eTCyVEewIZzvYgDg4QC5Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Although the people who work here are very kind I can’t recommend them as a new patient. My first appointment with them I ended up waiting 45 minutes in the waiting area until I finally asked the front desk what was going on and the man who helped me said “have you been waiting out here this whole time?” He then went to get someone else. The operations manager finally came over and said the dentist had a procedure running longer than expected and asked me to reschedule for a different day. It seemed as if they’d just forgotten me but I understand things happen. The second appointment I get back into the room get some pictures and X-rays and then the operation manager comes in and says yet again the dentist had a procedure run over and wouldn’t be able to do my cleaning. When I went back up to the front he tried to reschedule me for over a month away. I am at this point overdue for my cleaning and have now wasted two different days taking time off work for nothing. I will not be going back here and would not recommend them if you’re a new patient trying to find a new dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Pickett Orr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIznU3aronuKrCY9tzfKWkJeZpXswMfC5O3TbLNQqnzxAYZuX0YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been seeing Dr. V at Crown Hill Dental for about 2 years now. It’s such a great experience all around: From the office staff, to each hygienist, and of course Dr. V’s kind and thorough care. Each visit I receive helpful recommendations to improve my oral hygiene. I highly recommend this team for dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dolly Llama","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbUnrtjlXWBoA4FMaid-kGFMEo0JVqHpPv9rmKxP95Y5JZq-_K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It's a good practice, but I've had way too much difficulty getting an appointment. Even after booking them months out, they cancelled my last visit just days before and rescheduled me for six months out. Very disappointing.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
