:""},{"Name":"A Ellis-Noonchester (Al)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJe26u9owqG9TlgO3ms_i6LF-hDyg-f_kEF68C4mn_XXGMmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Didn’t take long to get a new patient exam with Dr. Tabaraie. I needed to get clearance to have some medical treatment, and I was seen within a week. Exam, X-rays, cleaning, and some needed replacement fillings were all accommodated in one appointment. The staff was caring and efficient with both their time and mine. I loved the professionalism and quality care that I received at Lakeside Dental. The new office looks great and was easy to find. I also loved how thorough each procedure was. The entire office was very inviting and friendly. I would highly recommend Dr. Tabaraie, if you are looking for a compassionate and extremely qualified dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Layton Wakatsuki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcYQj8m6PLvcDd3AXQnp-2C6Di_5oq6xl9QEs48sqoqyVbJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Six month check up in Lakeside’s clean new Wedgwood digs. Dr. T filled a cavity then personally did my cleaning. She alerted me to higher than norm tartar build up. Appreciated the red alert as i had no idea. Scheduled a three month check back to re-assess. This is the type of detailed and careful dental care I’ve come to appreciate from Dr. T.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Apollo Lira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR-oFBa8d7TuqDL5LZIlGg3TsiiAO7Qm7VYvvhM_7TVZ5cZxikCw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really like it here. The staff are great advocates, insightful, and very easy to talk to. I feel like I'm getting some the best dental care out there by a very caring and professional team of people.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Ording","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiypXu-tKx3onMzYLwMCGGjkpvjqQcELjF4bohxMsAHYnHtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadn’t been to the dentist in a long time. I was randomly driving by Lakeside because it was near where I lived. I couldn’t have made a better choice. Everyone there was fantastic! I highly recommend them..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvHg2ajDot-cIIP29H-rrDk7td1o3HonnmyVuRUGhCaeEpR_o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Lakeside Dental Center for over 20 years! Dr Shokofeh Tabaraie has been there for all 3 of my boys from their first teeth. She is an absolute gem, and I highly recommend her and her team to everyone I know!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristin Riemedio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlGl1owvOQjLoBrUZghhWTCU5fPV4I75dtnmEBrlZ-xu0MOGGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Tabaraie and her team operate like a well-oiled machine. I came to them with many dental issues and they have stewarded me through the process with compassion, patience and an expertise in their craft. I trust them and I feel well taken care of as a patient there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Reid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1WIcdl2cjNnPbu5S61pV0Zkwtc8dRXaddzjhCJIwn45jVGfEc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lake Side Dental is hands down the best!\nDr. Shokofeh Tabaraie is one of the kindest, smartest, and most talented dentists you’ll ever meet. She’s not only a perfectionist but also a true artist when it comes to creating beautiful smiles. She treats her patients like family and always goes above and beyond.\n\nI’m often asked how my teeth look so great, and the answer is always the same—Dr. Tabaraie and her incredible team. They are truly the best, and you will not be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
