ss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzf0Td_VN36u87rTVJ5rkFhq0w6Ha1MArL7H_sG-TAtfaCpY8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down one of the best, if not the best, dental experience I’ve ever had (no pun intended - they’re aptly named). The staff was extremely friendly and supportive, and checked in regularly to make sure I was comfortable and still doing okay. The doctor explained things clearly and thoroughly, and the office itself was clean and comfortable. Would absolutely recommend this office and the doctors here to anyone, especially those with dental fears or anxiety.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX34RUfK635H7TYIZr12hhUltVcjXR2xYa5MI0fT8_0ZXZSfl3q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going here for a while now and they are honestly the best dentists office I've ever been to. They are very nice, and have handled all my cleanings and fillings in a compassionate kind way. I'm not nervous about the dentist but my husband is and he was the one who recommended them to me.  The front desk is very good at communication and have been very understanding when I've needed to reschedule. Overall definitely would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjyPEBSkuUPZ1xUjHeWhnXnmPX36BnVGCTHkym5oN4tgxK5IZl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today was my first appointment and I have only good things to say! The entire staff was authentically friendly and kind. The place is just the right size -- not too big, not too small. It's clean, the equipment is modern and in good shape. My appointment was effective and professional. The TV monitor played a channel with funny pets that made me laugh. I actually enjoyed the experience and left smiling. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MaryGrace Katusiime","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJnu9Q2QVOe7mvUWDGdaIn6t_k7Kly5PzASXoL--i0ojWmohB6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was just my first visit but it felt very positive, respectful, and safe. The whole experience had an uplifting tone. Dr Ruben was kind and did a great job explaining the work I need to get done. I look forward to continuing my care with this team and already so relieved I made the switch!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grace Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwqiVGnB-98x7Wdw_3z2t-EmybE8Ic9TDLhZo2fY4hXqGrfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the employees are lovely! The dentist was friendly, knowledgeable and careful. They were able to provide new insights that I wasn’t aware of, even though I’ve consistently gone to another office every 6 months. Glad I made the switch over here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julia Guard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBjDSO0SexP42RoNyvVgrSaiknGh2HChmm6QKdwbuaV-mQZXK0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed to find a new dentist and happily came across Best Dentistry. Dr. Yeung was terrific.  Quick cleaning, thorough and took the time to listen.  Everyone was super kind and polite.  I definitely will be coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"natasha nuaimat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmIRGkjPqBvUWt2iASERf0zXix1C2QXQEnphWShds7VoqPzJEa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best experience ever at Best Dentistry! From the moment I walked in, the front desk staff a very kind young woman and a helpful gentleman provided the best customer service I’ve ever had at a dental office. They were welcoming, professional, and made the whole visit feel smooth and stress free.\n\nThe doctor and his assistant were equally amazing gentle, patient, and made sure I was comfortable throughout my treatment. I truly felt like I was in great hands.\n\nThis office goes above and beyond in every way. I highly recommend Best Dentistry to anyone looking for a dental team that truly cares about their patients!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tessa R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAdiYVC4cylPNe4W5rFb-4rWHz1aGiAQNR3VE82MEwr_uGjlk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried a couple dentists in Seattle over the past decade, and am SO glad I landed with Best Dentistry. The staff is super friendly and informative, they advise on work without pushing for unnecessary stuff, and they play animal videos as a nice distraction while your mouth is filled with scary instruments. 10/10, will be a happy customer as long as I live here.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
