ad of its time.\nWow.\n\nCheers\nLarry Lee Palmer\n\n.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj9D5aEUYzVG-RGR-lsWGgWdXBK-lUGXxIPeJzN2xJk5ITi9KX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a paitent of Sage Family Dentistry for more than five years now and have had multiple procedures from replacing old fillings, crowns, chip repairs, cleanings and regular checkups. Each time I visited this dentistry, I'm greeted in the reception area, and sit comfortably for a short time before being escorted into a bright and private room with the most recent technologies.\nI continue to goto Sage Family Dentistry because I love my smile now and can hold my head up high with confidence knowing I made the right choice making this dentistry for my adult teeth. And hey, Dr. Sage sent me a hand-written thank you card after my first appointment. That to me, confirmed my decision to continue referring people and my checkups.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie Daniels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWO3hTMoOoZNL7kq9ib50mvPkQDQp0M05IlvuaWupHkuUizJFU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had many dental cleanings in my life, but without a doubt The last three I have had at Sage dentistry have been the best. Julia knocks it out of the park. She listens educates and and genuinely improves the health of my mouth. She gives me great confidence through her knowledge and professionalism. And she’s a lot of fun!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debra Jarvis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNbwOGUi6SlH6QNVxHA8FXVsYFo116TbSgY4e1LvQmhWOkFA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Skilled dentists who LISTEN, gentle, thorough with a beautiful office which is the cherry on top. I had a complicated extraction, bone graft, implant situation and really appreciated that Dr. Sage referred me out because he didn't feel comfortable doing it himself. No big egos here. I totally trust him and his staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Myers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-ZjbuNz9lL6yo6OywCnQDd-tEsJL1uEbzyS9jJ6xzAzLzxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My Hygienist is fabulous. Sage can actually make going to the dentist fun. Great atmosphere and they educated me on things I didn't know (water pik importance). Pulled it out of the cupboard. They care and it shows.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2A6qRJ4_6z4l5XhLm2f4mTzhxqt5N_FasVA7QQUYv0m_tiKWEBWchXnZcwNbzP42e1-PZTYdkhrxK-CF4Wi1TE4TRf4jFUsDaI7TScfJx-SyZ4gnpoPCe8IXgy9HM4l6Wf_YA=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-1"},{"Name":"Paul Eriks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocII4WTWPbxIs2ucBtRd-hv1SN1rsGn9FFv88UAZuI85u1iXEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I left tent yesterday with a smile on my face.  Not only did I get a very thorough cleaning if my teeth by Julie, during her visit with me the dentist  told me she had read my chart and asked how I was doing since mr wife's death.  I was treated as a person and not a patient.  Good going.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
