re I’m comfortable and does a wonderful job. I’ve had to get my retainer replaced and the whole process went smoothly, very happy with the results. I recommend them to anyone who needs a dentist. A special shout-out to the lovely front desk people who warmly welcome you in every time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Astrid Sicola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGkn7VLWzYoChJkDAocoQuvVHOBzv04zJF3JI9magDtE1clYiH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can not say more than has already been said by previous reviewers, that Seattle Smile Works is amazing. The office is a bit dated, and I was worried when I first arrived that the care would be similar, but I couldn't have been more wrong. The dentist and dental assistants are amazing, they are all up to date with the latest dental protocols, and are very, very thorough and thoughtful. Couldn't recommend them more","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
