me":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Daniel Haghjou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX-N77e3mOmjLW1psRRAk_hCN62v7mYkMsZPIo71oqWTEfCwb-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. He and her entire team are absolutely amazing. I’ve always had a great experience here. Dr. He is attentive, caring, and genuinely warm. I also had a wonderful experience with Delaney, one of the hygienists—my teeth feel and look noticeably better afterwards! The front desk staff are consistently kind, patient, and attentive as well. I highly recommend this office :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annika Previs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5Cv4ARjX0mBrtBub4lFWiSe76gOH_xTQOTaDDYWCXTSjCrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Being a new patient at a dental office can be so intimidating and nerve-racking, and I was absolutely dreading it! I hadn’t been to the dentist in a while because I had felt judged, embarrassed, and pressured into treatments at my last dentist, but all that anxiety started to slowly (and cautiously) disappear throughout my appointment at Ballard Dentistry. I am incredibly impressed by and grateful to have found them! They were kind, thorough (in cleaning and with education/info), and I left feeling well taken care of. I know I’m just some person on the internet, but I highly recommend and encourage you to be brave and check them out!! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Max Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKc_tCkMx1NYV4n91_SLJ427rzfkadxWd36sVUneVUixmWj3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In one visit I’ve felt more comfortable, heard and optimistic in my care at every point in my appointment than I have my whole life receiving dental/medical care. It was quick to get an appointment as well as the follow up for the procedure I’m urgently in need of. They provided straight forward realistic options that has made me, someone who has not been taking care of themselves for sometime now and was dreading going in, feel hopeful and excited to start getting these things fixed. Never thought I’d say this, but I’m looking forward to going back to the dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa K.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQezGKZ1C-6URwF9YYtTDVHMpzp_fRJIajgDzhEmUiMTSGHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I feel compelled to share my positive experience with Ballard Dentistry, Dr. Jing He, and her entire office. As a person who has had several negative dental experiences in the past, I was amazed to find such a caring, compassionate, and professional team at Ballard Dentistry. Dr. He has been my dentist for several years. She and her staff have gone to great lengths to ensure my excellent dental care, comfort during each procedure, and assistance with insurance claims. The entire team integrates high technology with simple procedures to ensure the most positive outcome, and the restorations and crowns I have received are excellent. My family and I have complete trust in Ballard Dentistry and the kind professionals who work there","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S Lea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1ZcuaKmjRnxbMg0HzO7xlFh1gojj7rfgAjRTrnulw_8Boog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great first experience here with Dr. Jing He. She was very considerate of my TMJ/jaw issues as she worked. She seems very professional and takes the time to explain things thoroughly. Would recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Hughes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQGVTxWTS8AiHj83AcUor8_7Q-vVlOvYTKXqMiP8YUWVG87t-mxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely loved my appointment today (first visit) The staff were amazing and Doctor\nStreiff was extremely knowledgeable, gentle and informative. I couldn’t be happier… Billy Hughes","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morgan VanFleet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPytrkNMIpbZ8Qgd88nAu4JQnit_hTu7XMI--b_zRVQi5kpJQr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. He was extremely thorough, and explained the issues I’ve been having in a clear and easy to follow manner. The front office staff and hygienist were also welcoming and professional. I was well cared for, and they validated my anxiety around dentistry while helping me feel more comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig Mcdonell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK69-vd9td_IhqX2l7KnojkNHEkY1rqh71iqm8nWIkuCfImpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly efficient visit at Ballard Dentistry! I was taken back right on time, and the cleaning was quick yet comprehensive. Finished in 45 minutes with clean teeth! Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
