,{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Chloe Lynn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYX-r4abxRuTTvlIAm4gg-gXTWp1VIK80daa_-DhPiv7AefA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve always been really scared of going to the dentist, but this office completely changed that for me. Everyone was so kind and patient from start to finish. Stephanie at the front desk was incredibly caring and went above and beyond to comfort me when I was nervous about signing up for treatment. The hygienists, Minn and Lohimaa, were gentle, patient, and made sure I felt comfortable the whole time. Dr. Pederson was professional, explained everything clearly, and had great bedside manner. I never felt rushed or pressured, which made such a difference. I also appreciated how pricing was transparent so no billing surprises. Highly recommend, especially if you’re someone who gets anxious about dental visits.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Manzano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1SUcH41r5NVsFj8UGKhNQCql1iIs-q5pQpAd4DBLkVzY_8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my second visit and I had two cavities fixed by Dr. P. She has been super amazing! I have a fear of the dentist and she has made it such a great experience for me. She did a great job at making the injections feel less painful than usual which I appreciate.\n\nOn my first visit, I had a great deep cleaning by Min and the manager Stephanie was able to assist and help me figure out a payment plan to be able to get everything I needed done. I'm finally getting my wisdom teeth done!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW037kQ1KjGgb_DXCPQHXS19mXWj8K1OaQO6yz2E7y8hyQzyU4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a really good experience (as usual) at South Lake Union Dentist Office. It is a professional and modern office with friendly and knowledgeable staff.\n\nI have been coming to Dr. Pedersen for a few years and recently went in for a regular cleaning. Dr. Pedersen is thorough, easy to talk to, and took the time to walk me through a few different options for my teeth. My dental hygienist Grant was awesome as well and worked quickly and efficiently.\n\nDefinitely recommend if you want a dentist office that’s on top of it and doesn’t make dental visits more painful than they need to be!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yangje Sherpa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhxBabBSiFczZDspNVMgrz8xnW6wq82gCxZzMC8w6XOFx4SPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I fell off a lime scooter on a night out, chipped three of my front teeth and was soo stressed out. I went to two other places and got some quotes, and as someone with no dental insurance I really had to search for affordable options. I was referred to this place by my friend who also goes here and they were so kind to me, and was the only place besides UW Dental that offered a payment plan. I wanted to get the procedure done sooner than later so I wouldn't be afraid to smile without a mask on, and the receptionist Maxine helped me get in as soon as possible. I booked an appointment for Tuesday, but she called me and let me know that she was able to squeeze me on Monday which I am so grateful for. Dr. Pedersen was the doctor who helped me out and gave me a lot of reassurance about my situation. She told me she had the same thing happen to her with the lime scooter, and her teeth looked pretty good so I knew I was in good hands. I told her about the other dentist that I went to, showed her the proposed treatment plan that was $17,000... which is absolutely absurd!! She told me that they were trying to take advantage of me by adding on extra things that were unnecessary. In this economic climate, it's difficult to find a business that will be honest with you and not try to scam you for some more money. While I don't go to the dentist consistently, I definitely recommend this place to anyone who is looking for a dentist, or has a dental emergency. 5 Stars!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alina Shamina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyrpIft4Wk1PPJ6rEo_kJG_KmlDgXLTNQgD0abBsf4MzMGy2vU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Did annual tooth cleaning with them. First time with the dental assistant, a few weeks past- started getting weird spots in between the teeth. I never had them before, got scared. Called to book an appointment and they took me no problem. The dentist himself did a cleaning and changed the cleaning paste. I would put more stars but the perfection is in details. By the end of cleaning my face was covered in the paste, the little clothes covering cloth was on the floor, my shirt was wet.  I mean, I hope my teeth will stay white( as I’m still not sure what went wrong the first time) but the overall experience was just ok. BTW the front desk ladies are great (added a star just for them)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaime Orozco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV91yzX3fj7OU5tszdhlUlEGzCMqmFjAxxlU0KrVn4t17gVbdR8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ghaly from the very moment I sat in her chair, she made me feel completely comfortable and at ease. Dental visits can sometimes feel stressful, but Dr. Ghaly has such a calm, reassuring presence that all of my nerves disappeared almost instantly. She took the time to explain everything she was doing, checked in with me throughout the appointment, and made sure I was comfortable every step of the way.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn20bnKo32aeIgOnzvvAvZuLTDORAFLOePVMigVnVFOoNTGPgrIYvoTe-AvaMVh8uO4q1W3ZS5MyDZWJzm3TVX1roNNTencZFgV55fX0ODOrc9CJLrgp6DuA89wpAjo6VSJKI9dgln0iN0I=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Chiakanma Osuala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdFZp1njeWigZxf8smR088_QbcYFWMHltnCnmqRe0wzy9XUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely LOVED my time here! Was treated with so much hospitality and care right from when I walked through the door. Professionalism at its best! Celisha and Steph at the front desk attended to me and they were very helpful with all I needed to know regarding insurance and were totally wonderful with the level of service overall that they provided! Dr. Z and Izzy were also remarkable, and I am happy I chose this place as my dentist office! Would 10/10 recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annelyse Uwera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVnkeD1-ZFTnc_yfOyXHrPSAlIa4iUr9w7cC877j0y74bREA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently saw Dr. Z for a wisdom tooth extraction, and I can confidently say it was the best dental experience I’ve ever had. I was in a lot of pain and he was incredibly proactive about getting me in right away. From start to finish, he was so gentle — I quite literally didn’t feel a thing during the extraction, and I had almost no swelling afterward.\n\nDr. Z took the time to explain everything clearly, walked me through what needed to be done, and was patient in answering all of my questions. It was a refreshing experience, especially after having seen another dentist just days before who tried to quote me an exorbitant amount and even suggested unnecessary procedures. Dr. Z’s honesty and genuine willingness to help immediately put me at ease and earned him a new loyal patient.\n\nI just moved to Seattle, so finding trusted providers has been tough, but I’m so grateful to have found this office. The front desk staff were just as pleasant and helpful, and they worked seamlessly with my insurance. No more being scared of the dentist — I’m actually excited for my visits now! Plus, the office is conveniently within walking distance from my job.\n\nHighly recommend to anyone looking for quality, honest dental care.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
