g6Yw0m9uvBPq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for my cleanings and found they did invisalign! I was very very satisfy with my results! Been a regular patient since.\n\nThe team is friendly and knowledgeable. My smile has never looked better!\n\nDr. Park is very gentle on my sensitive teeth. I am usually anxious about the dentist, but Dr. Park works hard to accommodate me. I highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connie Moffit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXPapFKP2bcNRK6EUXpdF9TefvPF7IC092R-DNOFj1l-3bEQM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy to rate Spark Dental highly!  Dr. Park and Liz provide excellent dental care - they're skilled, gentle, and always communicative and friendly.  I've been particularly grateful for their help figuring out dental priorities in light of insurance limitations and personal cash flow. They genuinely help the 'whole' person, not just a walking set of teeth. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4mh57NYn0Spee8yNSJARxT8YSULXAhmQzsfIZS7boNi_78w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist in town. Dr. Park is so nice and does an excellent job. Staff is nice as well. My experience with other dentists led me to feel that a lot of dentists are not trustworthy, but I trust Dr. Park 100%!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Pak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBspBjDoFVJyA8BzL6A6olCj4nGzhzBMcRoVU0BgiAzbpI6Hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to Spark Dental for years, and always have a fantastic experience. The entire staff is warm welcoming, and incredibly professional. Dr. Park is thorough, gentle, and makes you feel completely at ease. I have very sensitive teeth/gums, and they do some of the most comfortable cleanings I have ever experienced (yes, I said comfortable!)\n\nHighly recommend