ng to the dentist is never fun, but I enjoy seeing them when I arrive for my appointments. Highly recommended!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXVdWxMuk4ltlWCitKyN3o9I5LgFJBsBut9jtSfAcJZMCbpgnh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"High levels of infection control, skillful staff, and Dr. Harvey is both compassionate and extremely gifted as a dentist. I have been her patient for 23 years and would go nowhere else. She and her staff also made caring accommodations for my neurodivergent ex spouse, making a tough experience doable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kurt Pachaud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5lV447ISr_wscc1EctjMBR6m7ceEYHXbDcpW33Nfs-CAA0oKD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and Dr Harvey are all really great with prompt service and very mindful of my time.\nThey got me in fast as my tooth was feeling pretty sensitive. They have fairly new machinery with digital imaging. Parking is usually available on the side streets for free.\nGreat location in a fairly new building on Greenwood avenue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Heisey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkjirX4kMHI7VauRCUhYcNIIFAO4lx_tuHonox4WP8cOMN3pL1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I would not recommend this dental office. My experience was disorganized, unprofessional, and ultimately cost me far more than I was originally quoted.\n\nI first met with a doctor for a consultation about having my wisdom teeth removed. They took X-rays and quoted me about $500 total for the procedure. I scheduled the appointment but never received any follow-up communication before the surgery date.\n\nWhen I arrived for my appointment, the staff began with panoramic X-rays and then led me to another room, where I met a different surgeon—who didn’t even seem aware that I was scheduled for a wisdom tooth extraction that day. He began numbing my mouth, and while I was partially numbed, another staff member came in with a form for me to sign. I assumed it covered the same procedure I had previously discussed.\n\nThe procedure itself felt rushed and uncoordinated. The assistant seemed inexperienced, and there was no aftercare information or instructions provided.\n\nTo make matters worse, at checkout they charged me $2,500—five times the original quote. When I asked about the charge, I was told the doctor was unavailable and that I’d receive a call later in the week. They wrote my number on a sticky note, and no one ever called me back.\n\nThis office shows a serious lack of communication, transparency, and patient care. I left feeling completely taken advantage of. Because I signed their form (while numbed and mid-procedure), I’m apparently stuck with the bill.\n\nPlease avoid this office. The care is inconsistent, the staff is disorganized, and their billing practices feel misleading and predatory.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Furstenberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsiD6b9MyuDGkPTJAUHyZdwsGQ_gLMAfozVa-HYuFPHinbEFkd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family has been going to Dr. Harvey for our dental care for more than 20 years.  She is an excellent dentist who has very high standards for her dental work and also is very compassionate if you have dental fears.  Urban Dental is a fantastic place for dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"deb chase","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKb4pwIvRfofVFX8rsXNs2d1XYLkQ1e8I6FCTHvLmGOWI87Jg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first visit with Urban Dental Group located in the Greenwood location.  I’d highly recommend them for a friendly relaxing environment and caring professionals who were efficient as well.\nThank you Urban Group Team for an enjoyable experience today!\nDeb","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Micah Greenberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWRavpu4ldgH5ZRfMncwDVirV9MBcJdhn7PCS02D5QHbThUSNO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been receiving excellent care from the Urban dental Group for more than two decades. I am grateful for the excellent chair-side manner \u0026 outstanding Staff. I would recommend this top notch Group to everyone who needs a new Dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yim Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNsPOYpO-gSEZ0WEVL1mQR4E8TR9OLTwIrCXFHM5xTczmohg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff at urban dental was great. Especially Rosie and Becky. I had some issues with my mouthguard and they were quick to help  me setup an appointment to get it replaced. Everyone there is friendly and attentive!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
