r questions and ease concerns. Dawn at the front desk is also fantastic. Always kind, prompt in communication, and helpful. Thank you Dr Martin and Dawn! I appreciate you and all that you are doing at Keystone Dental for me, and the wider community.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe Fitzgerald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKszHpHvdJift6uRwcwoKO10U0yvISdRg2rFeREh30THD3B8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am 85 years old and have sat in a few dental chairs over the years. Keystone dental is by far and away the best I have ever been to. It of course it starts with the dentist himself. Michael Martin is the absolute best! He uses the state of the art equipment He has an equally top notch staff as well - from the receptionist to the dental hygienist!\nWhat a wonderful experience! No reason to be apprehensive of going to the dentist ever again as long as you go see Mike and his staff at Keystone Dental!!!! - Joe Fitzgerald.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Betty Cargill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpWtdDlG81IIymcMvbasYXUAILbCQG6zRTNm6om6oDt6FX89_9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Keystone needing urgent care. Dawn got me in right away and Dr. Martin spent a half hour just listening to me describe how I’d lost a tooth due to an ill-fitted bridge (that broke, snapping a tooth with it). Before he even examined inside my mouth he placed hands against both sides of my jaw having me open and close. He thoroughly measured other characteristics of my bite scope to conclude that I was never suitable for a bridge at all, thus the horror. I am deeply grateful to have Dr. Martin’s expertise, to finally know WHY I had suffered tooth loss, a failed bridge etc; to know that I can trust Dr. Martin will deliver a truly reliable diagnosis \u0026 solution. Highest credit to Dr Martin and his lovely team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Curti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX40XcvDFc-VQgOkqhA3GnS5dxZQnq89lqek7h-t1piLyNNev0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So happy we made decision to move dentists to Keystone Dental. They took added time to gain information on both global history of my dental interventions as well as high level medical health before start of appointment. I was treated with great care by both Dr. Martin and Laura thru my initial visit. Gained good insight of areas I needed to focus on for my daily care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Micki McGuire","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHIBfFtrF_UXI0COTeLiz1xTrMizv8xFHzzcUzeWpxOSb0qg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Please accept my thanks for the good experience. I join those whose hair catches fire at the thought of any medical or dental intervention.,The dentist and  hygienist are proficient, kind and gentle; the receptionist was extremely efficient and nice. Thank you for your professionalism. My hair is intact and, again, I am grateful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tara Katz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq2ZWzSH98Ljmul9hVkUxXQo3S_pdqoXxvarZap5Ro-8rD-Ktb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Michael Martin and his dental team. I have been a happy customer for years and have zero complaints, only compliments. Laura is a fabulous hygienist. I feel very lucky to have found such a great Dentist and Co.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"torrey hay john","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAmHRMD0hBlT5KESkYRq_XBtzRYy4eXgQSUNvspR0VQ0JdExel=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff. Skilled, friendly, and always up on the latest research. Dr Martin and staff are always helpful at communicating what is going on in a way I can understand, letting me know what they recommend, then non-judgmentally empowering me to make my own decisions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Remy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJz3W_7DQrjVcraK_677gQUQzl0JGr6ctMofIa7zThwzNF6VQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a small chip in my front tooth restoration. Called them and they got me in first thing the next day. Repaired it like new in 20 minutes and I'm out the door. They're the best. The Best.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
