vations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"106722525851584190972","name":"Lake City Dental Group (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106722525851584190972"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Cedar Park","street":"3340 NE 125th St","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98125","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kimberly Bevier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeb-ZUMk_PHhtG5mQdxlg3S29davQQhTcZ2dzXyXJodgYkCXlZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Cheng and his staff are so kind and welcoming. I had such a great experience, even just getting my teeth cleaned and examined! Wonderful people.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yamili Marquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWfCjXoUi33_m9_pYPf7NYYuDKls01F7CwMyrUSgxUYg9WtddZWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the whole team. I know I'm being cared for every step of the way. I used to have major anxiety about going to the dentist, until I started seeing Dr. Cheng. They have the sweetest dog, which instantly calmed my nerves. I have so many questions and they always take the time to thoroughly explain. Communication is outstanding. I never feel any kind of pressure or unease. I now live in Rainier Beach and will gladly drive up to an hour in traffic to see them. Its such a wonderful service they provide.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel J. S. Pendragon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-oEg_xVyEXe5OWr_NSFGplStQY4-Qh732Hn7BHvhFpVotUNc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This might be the best dentist I have ever been to. Dr. Cheng and his hygienist are both very nice, friendly, and gentle. They are straightforward and explain what they are doing and what you need. I didn't have to sit around in the waiting room forever. They were willing to work with me cost-wise after I changed jobs and lost my dental insurance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Helene Israel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHEt0FWtgcJ10ji41UAlvMD8HKzBYA31XXEISOiN5lJrVy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been to many dentists in my 67 years but for the last 5 years I have held on tight to this one. Not only is this dentist kind and very caring, he is very good at what he does. Plus, which is important to me, his shots to numb have not hurt me!  He’s young enough to know all the new ways of doing things, yet old enough to have much experience and professionalism. The office staff are all so friendly and caring and try to help in every way to fulfill my needs. After hours, on an emergency, he has dropped everything and met me back at his office. (And he didn’t make me feel guilty all 5 times on this one mean tooth!). Plus, and most important to me who is on a fixed income, his prices are much more reasonable than most. You will love having Dr. Cheng as your dentist.  I know I do!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Ivy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrmwRGSIBnb7i2lQ3k1bY6vppTuC7r2qpyQ23zHzGlfn1CEoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Dr Cheng and his staff! Wonderful and caring, it felt amazing to finally have a regular dentist I could trust. The only reason I stopped going to see him for dental care was because I moved across the state. If it wasn't for that, I would have never needed to find another dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK29jvQMb0MPw-Pd2QRdWZwQTJzSRya9RjyHPswX_RLBWI8AqPu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I am a long time patient at this dentist (over 3 years) but I am planning to switch now. My appointment was messed up by the front desk TWICE in the past few months and it’s really frustrating for me. I don’t know why this could happy aging and again. The first time nothing was remediated, and I had to reschedule to a much later time. The second time they were able to have me scheduled in the following week to make it work after I told them this was the second time! But I’m very concerned from now on, every single appointment, I have to do extra work from my end, making sure their job is done to book me in as what we already have communicated and my appointment is still there . Don’t want to deal with this hustle anymore.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rick Mullarky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUz0ORP_L3AQn0XnyU_MfA9teiaKaFpzh2jEsA8AvNEAHk_oJv7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really excellent experience with this dental office. Dr. Cheng is amazing at painless dentistry and great at explaining and discussing options. I have always intensely disliked going to the dentist and for the first time I've found it easy. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aimi I","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLT4LxqRNgb9hDIrdTefEY1MA9qFk6WawET4f9_Q6ik3BLuJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good service, efficient staff, and clean office. The doctor and the nurse were flexible for me and stayed well after office hours to work on my teeth. They were able to find the cause of my pain quickly, provided enough options and answered all my questions before doing any treatment.  They were also flexible with the payment plan which I am grateful for.  Great place!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
