also receive their dental care at Avila Dental. They also  highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracy A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqp2MabFTHj_WppbRziVFWHAB88QZwdcMxHNuASBRBmmFY3m0a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The clinical care is top-notch. My dentist was incredibly thorough, explaining every step of the process in a way that was easy to understand. They use modern technology and prioritize patient comfort, which significantly reduced any anxiety I had about the procedure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick McShane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVDY2k1VEKDxczVZaoZC9afZD6zSEl5Rpq0yrxfPYK-y7VjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I have been patients at Avila for years.  I encouraged her to come here because she has anxiety about going to the dentist and Dr. Bello and the staff here always are wonderful, kind and compassionate.  I have seen dentists before who seemed technically very competent but not one matched Dr. Bello's caring and considerate demeanor and practice.  I heartily encourage anyone looking for a dentist or who gets anxious about seeing the dentist to come here.  Dr. Bello happily will give referrals for more complex procedures like root canals, etc.  You can't go wrong here for excellent cleaning and basic maintenance care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisseth Navarro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNQopuFf0cnAXRqR3eKCGinkNzf6lTSsH4bmiumHPvAmn11HM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my first review for Dr Bello and her team. I just got my cleaning and I feel like evey tiny spot of my teeth was taken care. I feel like knew! I chose Dr Bello's because she speaks my native language.  And I feel like I can communicate my needs much better. I did invisaling years ago and was dealing with some gaps after that. Dr Bello suggested bonding to cover those gaps and they work pretty good. I don't have any more discomfort and I feel great. Overall,  I'm happy I've choosen Dr Bello's for my Dental heath and needs 🪻","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Meier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3JeFiY5HQnwF5H7PUgmeixg3c3WD0isFwtWe6sCeWO6s_zvmJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Bello and the Avila team have taken wonderful care of me for two years now.  They have very patiently and thoroughly answered the many questions I have about my teeth, and are full of technical knowledge and good advice about home care.  I also really appreciate the way Gabby recognized the unusual sensitivity of my teeth and adjusted my cleanings accordingly.  I highly recommend Avila Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alyson Mocarski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnImZikwcPxMeOunRmIxTYHNHPbc20K8SDPIeiVrsiX6bT_yyr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Avila Dental by a friend and they did not disappoint! On my initial visit, my childcare fell through so I had to come with my 4 yo and the staff was so kind to allow him to be with me and even checked in on him throughout my procedure. This was not necessary but incredibly appreciated. I am so glad to have found Avila Dental! They truly go above and beyond.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Dennison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_EetnH7JKmtKBqeelTdt01_PenddpQnMAwjlKZParNnJeoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had my teeth cleaned by Gabby. She was very gentle and answered all my questions. The early morning appointment worked great for my schedule. Dr. Bello checked my teeth and assured me that I was cavity free.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2i7TN4VmKhYNlEgRSIbHsji3SAx2TedVsoXP8tKND4aZ8KAKd6vXBvPaa-I9mt-IR4uXoIyWn3VnZF05cndg0JdV-jYorOAsINz9H3DCoKDFwRUKPTLmoUwIZcMed410GAWLz_=k-no"],"When":"2023-8-10"}],"user_revie