rance so I called and I believe it was Veronica who helped me and said she’d be at the stairs for us. Although it ended up being Brein.\nEveryone was extremely nice, fun, and friendly. Best dentist I’ve ever been to and my daughter definitely likes them as well.  They tell you everything they are doing, what needs to be done, and answer any questions we have. They talked to us as if we were old friends. The place is warm, cozy, and clean.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2cE51iRlBXohQ-4Ofx1QyHuUj2NS14fq02FAmg3IM06ZM8ZCAPsw3uULjlI1cvY3b9Qp_L6TdQQWaoTEGzdgEG3No22d7xEvyVStd3wfFFwYNIzXJaCR6pxQOFTRa3Ynj6bXJ3xfru5c-L=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn08cypTFL4Gg2AwsOVrz97FlczHtY65_RI0VXz9QYCFVMxgf1GTYlFxeZO2fJatL74jR6PkkBrWK6RW9SkMsCtekSTp2iRuPjZX5KC9ffW6owlYXj_RSJO2XN0AnoHrpdMlO2U_SaOt5GM=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-15"},{"Name":"Urvashi Pandey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvYY7yoDOen0Tkg3VXiBO_Yi6iupvItFNdv-3mYxsl7qe3xpgftQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the absolute best experience here! From the front desk to the staff and the doctor, everyone in the clinic is incredibly sweet and caring. They truly take the time to listen to you. Hands down, this is the best dentistry in Seattle. I will definitely be coming back and recommending them to all my friends and family!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tuyet Pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpzBTehCbyDYHvAEfA8XliW-vVy6JaSex7HYKnQKWWCn3XXjI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s was a good experience for me to have a good dentist’s visit with who I was interacting with. She was the best! So nice, so genuine in person. Explain everything to me in details so that i know  what is going to be done. The Doctor Who came out with a smile and was greeted with a welcoming. I thought that was very nice of her. Because that had never happened to me before. I feel so special and so grateful for her for being there. The office was so nice and clean everywhere. Everyone was very friendly, polite and helpful in their presence. I’m so grateful to my daughter who has been looking to found me a Dentist for the last couple of months!!!\nI would recommend for anyone who has been looking for a dentist to get their teeth cleaned, or fixing up the dental work for you!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alfred Broadbent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqqdpoFdXyxth3B8a0ZNWVVZOW7JZUzGLoNkimfoODR90uPuhU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the best dental practice I’ve experienced. Dr. Bertrand and her team have created a warm, friendly, and genuinely positive environment while delivering exceptional care. It’s rare in any industry to find a team that excels both in technical expertise and in thoughtful, proactive communication. They treat you like a whole person, not just a patient. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucy Maddux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWznPWkDI4MDFDEaNqimPd5QeOxXA2RfPSA7qV0HLciM0Fm11y7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this dentist office for the first time this morning as a new patient, and they were absolutely phenomenal. From the front desk manager, to the dental hygienist/assistant, and the doctor, every single person was incredibly understanding, compassionate, and professional.\n\nThey took the time to educate me throughout the entire process and offered anxiety-calming techniques that genuinely helped. I have never gotten through a dental appointment without immense anxiety—until today. That alone speaks volumes about the level of care and comfort they provided.\n\nI’ll absolutely be coming back routinely, and I highly recommend this office to anyone looking for a dentist who truly cares about their patients’ experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Madison Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUll8Nyl7vSSKdxht4jYwnxgtD-9nIyFSosRvynTROUiJ3XWHYk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience with this practice has been absolutely wonderful. Everyone I have interacted with has been delightful. They prioritize their client’s comfort and individualized care in a way that exceeds expectations. I have told anyone that will listen, “you gotta switch to MY dentist”.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Soper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuSpfI9S9jpkeWcJlOV3_OmPZD4w6OpZm6LOzEK7e0JIPhEmbjOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I honestly love this whole dentistry office so much!! I love all the staff - The hygienists have all been so lovely and the dentist is the best!! They all ask me about myself and will remember things from past appointments which is so nice. The lady at the front desk really seems like she knows how to handle confusing insurance situations and makes me feel in good hands. They all are so smiley and friendly. The hygienists asks you what type of music you want to listen to and you get dark shades to wear during the cleaning. They also have great goody bag items like Sensodyne which I know is a more expensive brand. The waiting room chairs are so comfy and the vibes there are just 10/10!! Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Maconachy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLF8YtnM_QxIWo3OdB6Vs3axC5hxl49gDGmHWyI67oYcwLcZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Dr Bertrand and all the staff! The dental work I have had here is well done, they stay up to date with latest technologies, they are caring and compassionate and really care about you as an individual patient! I have referred so many friends here because my experiences here have been so positive. Going to the dentist isn’t anyone’s favorite, but do yourself a favor and make it the best it can be and go to 2200 westlake!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_re