table before she starts work.  The permanent crown was placed yesterday and today it feels like nothing ever happened.  Professional, highly competent and just a nice person.  Her whole staff is capable and professional.  Plus, there is tons of parking!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPk0ZGwnSd_goE_UawB2HOfowgg23n4_ZZrbsUGl8revejaFM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Dr. Johnson years ago at her first practice and then I moved out of town for several years. I'm living back in the area and yesterday was my first appointment with her at her current practice in Northgate. She has managed to find herself an amazing staff, and I forgot how skilled she is as a dentist from executing tasks, to her amazing \"bedside\" manner. Unfortunately I have some additional work needed, but I know I'm getting the best possible dental care at her practice and now it's time to get some things taken care of! Thank you Dr. Johnson, Shay, Gillian, and Brooklyn, for the warm \"welcome back\". :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catherine M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfYoYxdWDBeolYB6WIxxcD4lSwIbN_Ig1oNl5Oj_hPycPHjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience. I have never had to wait longer than five minutes for my appointment. They are on time, friendly, and very customer service oriented. Location and parking is also great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelli Koon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9HzTgUw84tk1Beh2BC1UviqRBm4PQn8JExqYs87dIjL4BVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Johnson \u0026 her staff are so friendly \u0026 helpful.  I particularly appreciated their patience in answering questions \u0026 addressing my concerns.  I'm very happy she's my new dentist \u0026  I look forward to my next visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amber Staggs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPUKtJV9xop6OisZGqcGAuvHS-wjdvJ1hOSqcQIEjLl8JO6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always felt comfortable every time I sat in Linda‘s chair. She is very skilled and is pleasant to her patients. She stopped seeing me as a patient because i missed a couple of appointments and I was late one time. Because she canceled me as a patient, I ended up losing a tooth. I had a root canal that she had not capped. The tooth broke. I had asked her to finish what she started and my pleas were ignored. I dropped off flowers and candy. She didn’t have the decency to call me and say thank you. Again, I was ignored. I have always liked going into her office. I just wish we had a better send off. A call would have been nice. It still bothers me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Jacobsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrYHDs4uc-Tdjc_u7PRUGMtKlD0-qSBg_DD3mtzEYJV_5j92A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ginn is the best! I highly recommend her and the team at Linda Johnson, DDS.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine O'Hara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLls9LFLZ_oXa_MEw0PCIFz2B0vaEWq4y9dl8pIATOG53pMIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This team at Dr. Johnson's office is always excellent and go beyond what's  normally called for. No wait time. They double check the insurance source before you walk in and very concerned with keeping their patients comfortable during the procedure and don't try to pressure you for unnecessary work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
