l?panoid=aN3N7BFGQb70CgHuGDw0Mw\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=96.84003\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"113962514984211489224","name":"Roosevelt Dental Center (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113962514984211489224"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Roosevelt","street":"6417 Roosevelt Way NE #206","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98115","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Steven Lane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUle4Pf_9lrZpriUIbJ1SkPYIy-nVrbNrcTHrM7fzsRlP0FEz4v=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently moved to the area and needed to find a new dentist. This nearby 3 dentist office popped up with good reviews. I’ve now been in twice and my wife once. We have been quite pleased and plan to continue even though the office is not on the preferred (less expensive) provider list for our dental insurance. The office is clean, modern, efficient, and kid friendly.  The staff are super welcoming, personable, communicative and seem to be providing state of the art care. Good parking and pub trans access with many useful businesses nearby if you’re max packing your day.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Payton Reed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtOpro6eDUrl2Vod_ffIvxhI1PneW4njnO34Lx0rJyGqs9mJ60=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly thorough and considerate! I mentioned very minor teeth issues and they took my concerns very seriously. I felt very seen and heard during my appointment, and was well informed on the state of my oral health. The communication from the moment I stepped inside all the way to walking out the door was incredible at every level, from the front desk to teeth cleaning to the doctor themselves. The dentist office always makes me nervous, but I feel very well taken care of at Roosevelt Dental Center!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wei Xia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIODOzLzog4O9AcMofmY8NZZ5Kaob41mBmuQjfiSsfLcZZR2g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have always been scared of dentist since I had to go there often when I was a kid. But Roosevelt dental is so amazing that I think they just totally changed my perspective on going to dentist. Jeane (sorry if I misspelled your name) was very friendly and walked me through every detail and answered all my questions. She kept me company while I was nervously waiting for my result. Dr.Ko did an exam and fixed my cavity issue with great care. They did everything so smoothly that for the first time I feel like I m not anxious and don’t mind coming in again for more work. What I m most impressed with is everyone there is happy and the vibe is very uplifting. You can tell the place is good if everyone is enjoying what they do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Irvin MacQuarrie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu0LimTflZYXt54_6sSE5anQFurFcxMuqG2RSAqgDJEyHxgknB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I have lived on the east coast, I have had to go to a number of dentists and found nothing compared to Roosevelt Dental.  This has been the best dentist by far that I have been to.  The desk staff are friendly.  The hygienists work there for years and know what they are doing and friendly and remember you.  Dr. Gray is a high integrity dentist.  He monitors problem areas, but is slow to recommend expensive dental work although he would make a lot more money that way.  I wish I could find another dental experience like this.  Exceptional place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke Busby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5b8sZkP9pb5FeapCYOwkp_gDBjL9Ias0JqqUehfZy_mpUpFY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a wonderful patient experience when coming to Roosevelt Dental. Every member of the team is so incredibly kind and knowledgeable.  If you are looking for a new dental clinic, don’t settle for something below the standard, switch to Roosevelt Dental where they go above and beyond.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suzu Llewellyn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBUbS5z2P1FL7jj9tMQ1K9qlUN8bcgV1s-IYk9-XpxIlwmO0WD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been visiting Dr. Gray for over 25 years! They seem they are about our health and oral hygiene very seriously. Thank you for Dr. Gray and their stuffs to keeping healthy and good taking care me. They’re almost my family and happy that their business are successful growing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy VanBlaricom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFCbNWI-ZSItutaKVtxpleEu2xGdJMixLOGSLpWAyIA6cC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to Roosevelt dental and Dr Abedi after a complete disaster by another dentist.  I had a dental emergency that was caused by and literally blown off by my previous dentist.  This office got me in same day- efficiently and with clear concern and empathy.  The care I have received has been timely, appropriate, informed and without complication for the 4 visits I have had to clean up the previous mess.  I am eternally grateful to this office and have told my friends who are also physicians.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen Wroblewski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUTjFy3ZjYZunk706XoKr-qeoLG3NzlWsH0EG9ctullVDVrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly, caring and competent. The experts at Roosevelt Dental have been looking after my teeth and gums for 25+ years. The team also has taken care of my three kids from the beginning; they are so gentle and good at building rapport with young ones and teens alike. Clearly worth my loyalty!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
