throughout. Today my smile 😁 is perfect. Thank you so much. I'm a forever client and fan. 😁😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lavena Staten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJ11wPF_kwNc82wfN6j7tz5A6MCI84Q2JdUCdW-TgwJVX1nsX-Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"BEWARE!!! i went to this dentist office for three years. and every time i came in, i was told i have several cavities and i got them filled.\n\nlast time i went in, i was told i had six cavities that needed filled. i was suspicious and i decided to switch to another dentist because i take excellent care of my teeth and only had infrequent cavities before coming to A Dental \u0026 Denture.\n\nthe new dentist said i have ZERO cavities, nothing that even kinda resembled a cavity. sooooo take that into consideration if you go to this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theresa Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8itRpdOlr43RnbqirQ_KnupLbMWHvOt8U2o09t5AxG2vG9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Dental is wall to wall friendly, professional staff. They are great at providing dental care and always explained a procedure clearly and accurately. Anyone looking for a new dental clinic or looking to change their dentist, I would like to recommend this team of friendly and knowledgeable people for your dental care;  from cleaning to dentures you won’t be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Alspaugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOpMbwnnJYZAczJo3jWUCm92rq8Ned85bMsakaasLz_J7gE_9B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing job. Only took a few hours. Very nice staff. Can't even tell it was snapped apart widthwise across the middle. Reinforced with inserts. Probably stronger than it was originally.  I'm so happy 😊.  Wish I had taken a better picture of their very nice office. Update December 14,24 the dentures I had fixed are still perfect 👌","Images":["https:/