tead of making another appointment. he decided to put me back in there and fix it while I was still there. Took ten minutes and no charge. great place, wonderful staff, always helpful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kylie Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWElCnAIC2xPFvv4NlXHoj8RnFA75FSoXkBOvhL9k6ROUI53Iv4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw Dr. Amar for TMJ and a cleaning. Every step from the front desk associate, to the dental associate and Dr. Amar was fantastic. The dentist can be an intimidating experience, but they all were personable and knowledgeable. They didn’t push more than what you needed and I truly appreciate that. So grateful to have found them.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
