ions":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Maggie Barragan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHYvd1bEPMBHC_Izkx0vT_DZa-Kf2zEKkaV5JrBIcEZrYaApz_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent appointment today with outstanding customer service from everyone. Visiting this place for my follow-up was a truly pleasant experience. My dentist was fantastic, and the X-ray process was completely comfortable. Young man dental assistant was very professional and very nice. Highly recommend! You will like this place👏🏼","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abdul Rauf Muhammad Usman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUy5WzI1EtNiWUodOL7OpoQrf9kitWzMMC5HOOtO7quzjaEZ1m-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing staff and dental care. The reception staff, nurses and doctors are all the pretty awesome. They have always been helpful and caring. My dental cleaning, deep cleaning and fillings were all done within a short frame of time. And some sessions I only had some discomfort. Overall recommend this dental clinic to everyone. My only complaint is that there is an appointment cancellation charge and I always have some last minute things that pull me aside ;(","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0IDxzE4eWObJEA3UAz4cRCGONHZ2MpS1DAnSqTvnQTAmxLqPHACI8iosKcTWY_JtIsz4DlYQQC-102paEdH7Aj0Fw8e-a83rYMQ9gPCIOusEQrYNbzFo4ksemayR9b141Roa1j=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn17-arB_n7HnyF1zNMiixJOrcU9KYIv9QqluiKW3YPPgIJglKAAH39IJnPHaDjtpJjokP2WhUGrSvvYjFZm6ThKPa4JFB0cFO85DYw3ZgpaDMlo_KYKc2FsZRnS2u-6PY7_1atxVQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kxi023ttEtWBpFxML8DHH00BcBRlMHVTy0dwGtE_SBNm0O939GEreMR_Bti9Qc-hCdXYNy1unq7p58aVk-ADKOmPNF2KExkjbiketNSSSopG8XHlMQY_CjyjfgyIVXmODME_i=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2JWDQrOQBCVb5bxPSob5jzWWwT3zjoY8dnB3aV8SLfkMkhEhY3KYhwXoaOdv4IxsB7Rb7ZZgWxSnRGZffczqxKXmAsCeoE2g3kD-CCygVRTWYONvTvUdsZ8jhia_0puMIG4rlV=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Madeleine Laney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQ-BNpx4CQLd6NoV296HLi0aVjM9YVepdlC0zsBGvaPcgGpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming here for dental care 2-3x a year for the last 4ish years and I have had nothing but positive experiences. All of the staff I have interacted with are all so friendly and caring (I just got off the phone with them again which prompted me to finally leave a review). I feel heard and taken well care of when I come here, and they are sure to hear me out when I feel anxious or worried about the work being done. I recommend them to all of my friends and will continue to do so. Last thing to rave about, the dental care itself feels more thorough than any other dental provider I’ve been to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_TJY6zYSNkJnphTI-WbGsEmdQjLfMmlTelpsggTlcgTFgLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My grandpa is a patient of  the Greenlake Dental.   He mentioned he was taking my family to Tokyo Disney the other day.  Thanks to Amy  at the office who shared her recent experience waiting in line at a Disney for  long time.  As a result, my grandpa purchased grandparents  group package so we don't need to wait in line.  Thanks  a lot, Amy.   Sincerely, Ashley from Osaka, Japan.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria “Maggie” Barragan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTwtCJKnpym5oVoXsOBArnJ4NVeZbCZjuDFyi8185bhG5CYPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a fantastic experience at Greenlake Dental with Dr. Benjamin Chang. From the moment I walked in, the friendly and kind staff made me feel welcome and at ease. Dr. Chang took the time to thoroughly explain 😊 my situation regarding the molar I broke from grinding my teeth during sleep.( And practicing his Spanish was very good )\n\nHis detailed consultation about my options, particularly the process for a molar implant, was incredibly helpful. He made sure I understood every step, which significantly eased my anxiety about the procedure. I left feeling much better informed and confident in moving forward with the treatment.\n\nThe atmosphere at Greenlake Dental is warm and inviting, which only adds to the overall positive experience. I highly recommend this dental practice for anyone seeking excellent care and support. Thank you, Dr. Chang and the team, for making this experience so reassuring!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ZCPdYM15p7dQjbOhES-NkothTZS30d2uPaIvz0DKv9pXoD8ezFOwTuhN0SnTDwx8vszVaZnVvmZv-JMTmYN2K02jh_-Zccwl90DTdBC4LBY5mGdvZzu2Hid29PQfnA0DF20kuLoEgD5I=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-15"},{"Name":"Tiko Devidze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8jIVO3keS39t7zU3GxBzq9OO3LJmQkbjLTHGTZM0GDomrJtwZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Yaman is amazing. I had a huge fear of the dentist, but he made me feel totally safe and relaxed. If you are nervous, go see him!\n\nAlso, The girl out front is super friendly and made everything easy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Audrey O'Neill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ76uoQcfWyig4oT2IocVaYVvVnQm3Ix5xJBezzxf5KfTHa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have been coming here at least twice a year for 5 years, and for nearly every appointment, I have seen a different doctor and different hygienist. Because of this, every time I sit in the chair I am asked to re-explain my entire dental history, things that should already be in my chart and that they should be monitoring as my dentist. I think after 5 years I need to find a new dentist, because continuity of care is important to me, and I feel like I am not getting that here. The quality of the cleanings also varies wildly. Sometimes I feel like it was thorough, other times not as thorough. Everyone is very nice, but that's not my issue. I'm just very disappointed with the inconsistency of care and not sure what can be done about it. Would love to be booked with the same hygienist, or at least same doctor, every time, instead of this \"revolving door\" of providers as another reviewer called it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brianna Taylor Finley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGmflSNlyUxEHPrw2ylM7jo0KzGqS94VLtREqYKQ2fve9QFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love it here! Kalina, RDH, is so detailed I feel so safe with her and like she actually cares about my health from blood pressure to flossing. The front desk staff are also very knowledgeable, efficient, and kind. Would highly recommend for evidence-based, immensely high-quality care!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
