,{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Mama.H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTpoH5a7w0-Lcw_Kzyrz5Wxb3_WvZSoQtbunlcAxtc1LZipA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So far I am thrilled with my decision to become a patient here! I had my first cleaning today, and I was honestly blown away by how comfortable and pleasant the entire experience was. I have always hated going to the dentist, but Skylar my hygienist did such an excellent job with me. She was incredibly kind, gentle, and thorough. The office feels clean and upscale, and the staff seem happy! Definitely recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Caitlin Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFvyOIl_KUO7yzP6GIQAfjZ4EOUR_JD3rAc_NWxhC9BFlJEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Pietsch was amazing. I had a same day appointment with her and her team. I was in a lot of pain and I had to get a tooth pulled. I have a lot of anxiety around going to the dentist and she put me at ease. I also tend to not numb up very easily. She took her time during the appointment to make sure that I was comfortable and not in pain. I will be going back to become established as a patient. I was very impressed with her and her assistant. They were both lovely.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Honeywell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTqvW8oG8qOi6Nn5sEfjXEeKNpHJELLwfDkLjlNm-If_s-ow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Grace is an amazing hygienist- thorough and kind. All the dentists are great. Office staff is helpful and efficient. This women owned practice gives special touches like eye pads and warm towels when you’re done. You’re getting your teeth cleaned but feels like a mini facial😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayley L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjkHnXC061PmkWa-jw4jZJflbimdWTIe7JhHf1oMoViDyIal4xjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Could not recommend Floss more! I've had both Dr. Pietsch and Dr. Byun and both are wonderful. The staff are very friendly and great to work with. My dental hygienist Kat is so thorough and kind. She makes my cleanings feel so comfortable, and not a chore to go to. Their latest technology / up to date practices make it hard to imagine going anywhere else for care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Eshbaugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKB-BF_WNVerORBNjfVebv1eMJygxkmtT2zu0Mt2v5o-koQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient at Floss for a little under two years, which is sadly coming to an end as I am moving. That being said, since everyone else has already covered things seriously and in depth, I figured I would just have some fun with it, because it's my review, and not yours :)\n\nWhat would I say of FLOSS dentistry? She is... the mother I never had. She is... the sister everybody would want. She is... the friend that everybody deserves. I don't know a better dental office.\n\nAnd because gay people can't ever just compliment a woman normally or something like that, of Dr. Pietsch I would say, it is clear that every day she refills her Brita filter with the very waters.. of Mother Lake.\n\nSometimes bad things happen to you so that good things can come from it. Life has taught me that well. Were it not for me losing my retainer almost immediately after I got my braces off years ago, I never would've had the crooked and later chipped teeth necessary to begin at FLOSS when I most needed it. There's a lesson in there somewhere, folks. Learn something from this.\n\nAnd as I go off into the world, in the words of Alicia Keys all I have left to say is the same thing you will if you enroll at FLOSS which is: \"Wait 'til you see my smile.\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandi Adami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkX1XjyhiQ4xok1b5MNGSch8YMffirQ_owbd5tj6BMXTYpNMSr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have always had excellent dental care at Floss Dentistry, and have been a client there for too many years to count. Skylar was my dental hygienist at the most recent visit, and she gets rave reviews from me—she is knowledgeable, gentle, efficient, and taught me a lot of very helpful things. It is my pleasure to highly recommend Skyler and Floss Dentistry!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Khongor Jamiyanaa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzAg0SiU-PuwzsGfFEDXOe74HQau5krRYPUtE1YDy-82_loZU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently switched to Floss dental and I was very impressed by it all. Dr. Byun was very gentle and thorough. She found areas of concern that my last office didn't and also noticed I was flossing too hard in one area. She didn't pressure me, she explained all the options and the risks, gave her recommendation, and let me decide. Kat was also very diligent with her cleaning. The office was equipped with new instruments that was very easy on the patient. highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thren R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWizUbZUZPpSlQmpr1q3VfvcD0XVTM6m0G8HQww8oefoRE9APY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"when you call you actually get a person working there and everyone I've spoken to has been helpful, knowledgeable, and generally lovely. The work I've had there has been great, with care taken for comfort during and longevity after. They've gotten me in very quick when I had a concern and even advocated for me to get me into a trusted endodontist same day when I was in pain. Very happy with Dr Pietch and her staff","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
