},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Carolyn Kulb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcag6Y478nPfAYo0XOKtfKv8aFNkphjySOlXmx0H_dGXgfmgBV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Is it weird to love your dentists? I genuinely look forward to my dental visits, which was unimaginable to me before coming here. I have been a patient for years and through several insurance changes, and at this point I'd happily pay out of pocket. The Beths are amazing, the hygienists are gentle and conscientious (no ripping floss through your teeth like they are trying to start a lawnmower, no expecting a response with fingers in your mouth). I have also gotten excellent referrals to deal with some chronic dental issues. I wish all medical care was like this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marla Fields Stetina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8iIFH7Peu-cp6dqydr3tX5B_reu55uCemLEax572kW-wkGyMyXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had excellent dental care at New 32. Sunny is a fantastic dental hygienist—thorough, gentle, and friendly. Dr. Gilmore has been my dentist for many years and is truly outstanding. The entire team is warm and welcoming. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7Y8tUFbbhGwhxxs55R8dwF0l38tzhmzQAzCe4dfJqQGmp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sonny and Beth are the best. They have taken excellent care of my mouth for man years. I'm one of those people who look forward to going to the dentist. It feels like doing something really good for myself.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reid Winkler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTo17Arzb2vGUhcN9WqBTGwImTxla92VhnZTu1fwfpT1URiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm the orthodontist upstairs.  This practice is top notch.  If it tells you anything, it is the place I go for my personal dental care.  I've had the same hygienist for 15 years.  Feels like going to visit family.  From routine family dental care, to managing complex interdisciplinary esthetic cases, Drs. Shaw and Jacobsen are at the top of their game.  I am so fortunate to be able to collaborate with these true professionals.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fran Myer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5Yvmxbh0JbBVPOe1phiQjv6K-TcImnOBzxRa3mI5ImLrCVu9x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a tooth infection that needed immediate attention. Cindy managed to squeeze me in the same morning. Dr. J referred me to an endodontist for a root canal, and Cindy was able to get me an appointment there for that same afternoon. Efficient, professional, and effective!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bob McCrory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsmKXnmXiPAd7993TChudrwcmc6oOU7Z7HMIig5DntHF3kuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hygienist was professional, pain-free, and funny. One of my very best experiences in the dental chair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristen Klooster","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfdZH5iMyuPoiWmLD3IN3s7oIrEFGz83UhJZzxUB7WRsJiv-Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been going to New32 every 6 months for regular cleanings since my son was four (2021) and he actually looks forward to his dentist appointments! He loves getting to watch a cartoon while getting his teeth cleaned, which keeps him calm \u0026 still, he gets a new toothbrush each visit, and is always excited to pick out a toy from the treasure box at the end. I am so happy that he hasn't had any cavities with the excellent care \u0026 instructions from the team at New32. Highly recommend this office for the whole family, they are always on time, friendly, and professional.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0SW1Lshw1aoZdmnMW2mgQC70Sryg