onal and friendly too, the staff are only ever looking out for your best interests. I am very pleased with my experience here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L Tu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYUAp-VxK_kLhaLJtGW0AzlGgHs4stR_wpKiW4dFVpnlFv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got me in quickly to fix a crown! I only had been to this office once for a regular cleaning when a crown I had been having issues with popped off while flossing. I left a voicemail on their after hours line on Sunday morning - they called me back and got me scheduled to come in the next day.\n\nI had issues with that crown constantly after my prior dentist placed it, but it’s been over a week since Dr. Sohn fixed it and for the first time my bite feels normal again!\n\nThe office staff and everyone is extremely friendly too. I highly recommend this dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vahe Sahakian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyUAN-OWHg5YuJ-jCGvZvQ_mmIh2DWz-mQVZFOijb_7_VmzJI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I went to Emerald Dental during the year I worked in Seattle and we have been so happy with their work. Excellent and pragmatic dental care, lovely to deal with, very accommodating and overall just great. Can’t recommend them more highly","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annie Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoqF9w4CaeiIqJKXzPNC0tgN17mRiYBHOfGOYrBu3q9wAzz1_luQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this dentist office. Extremely helpful, very professional and knowledgeable. Both doctors are great and only suggest procedures, prescriptions etc if they really think you need it. They have your best interest in mind! They also just updated their office and exam rooms so new tech and very modern. Admin staff are great as well. Very easy to get in contact with and friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vance Roshler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkXysFtgGTZrK4vCcU5gQlmbALUT0AIbyED9yzm9QmcC6L_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming here for seven years.  I love this place.  Friendly, honest, trustworthy, helpful... just good people doing good dental work.\n\nAt my prior dentist (in another city), the care was good, but I constantly felt upsold, and prices routinely ran way past what my insurance covered.  Neither has been the case here.\n\nI rarely take the time to leave reviews, but these folks earned it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophia P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9BN5KQEJHNkP-c5lOvNfq22ucUlMuN_gN5l_ghLMSUi2FK6u-NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lisa at the front desk was so helpful and friendly, and took the time to reach out to my former dentist to get my most recent dental photos. Celeste the hygienist was very efficient and careful with taking photos since I mentioned my gag reflex sensitivity, and she was also very friendly. Dr.Brian was great and very thorough with my dental cleaning, and even though it was clearly a busy day he took the time to demonstrate proper flossing technique and discuss areas that I need to be extra careful with cleaning. Overall a very positive dentist experience — this office is a gem!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tatiana Tsives","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZb0D3CA0SPcbJ7ov6daDYMMUQVf0WHWhOoqXVyvMXlu3jeFr50w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient at this dental practice for over three years now, and I couldn't be happier with the care I've received. Dr.Katie is not only attentive and gentle, but they also make me feel completely at ease during every visit. It's evident that I'm in safe and capable hands. The staff is incredibly friendly and responsive, always going the extra mile to ensure my comfort. The recent office redesign and upgraded equipment have truly elevated the overall experience. I wholeheartedly recommend this dentist to anyone seeking exceptional care and a welcoming atmosphere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicolas Perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWldn_RB4GQz4pnhr3vEzji1j7Jy9mgqPIQrem_PMFU_vLW7uRV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely STELLAR staff. Very knowledgeable, explained everything that I should’ve had explained in all my years of visiting dentists at a level that was actionable for me. I left here knowing specific approaches to taking care of my oral health. Glad I chose them and I’ll definitely be returning here for all future needs!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
