6thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://www.patientsreach.com/schedule/2477aeba-9df3-11ef-813f-02812e505b51?referralsource=298","source":"patientsreach.com"},{"link":"https://api.leadconnectorhq.com/widget/group/9WwJTpJItHTtmIxzKRi2?rwg_token=AFd1xnHEQTLsCFI0YqWUTbNYz1JBX0QQsYc1qpyXp-M9xCy3EaKSi01GoHheP2gv4knXksRdz2rTTZNmR8eWBTVQ6phaWjFwpw%3D%3D","source":"leadconnectorhq.com"}],"menu":{"link":"/url?q=https://www.alkifamilydental.com/\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwj2rdCJpcSUAxW1ODQIHWb-Lv8QqRkIHSgQ\u0026usg=AOvVaw0EKgGlRszdIgsEeLwZtu3K","source":"alkifamilydental.com"},"owner":{"id":"107226275988550753387","name":"Alki Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107226275988550753387"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Alki","street":"1331 Harbor Ave SW STE 100","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98116","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Karleen Brigham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwUXzuEHy5uTwuS15qQLAk7Wg-Wf4bb1BbA17ytud5-JqOA0zPdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I just started going to Alki Dental. I had a price quote at another clinic on a Crown and it was outrageous and they didn't accept my dental insurance, so the cost would primarily be out of pocket.\nI decided to shop around. Alki Dental stood out for my needs. My quote  was way lower, and it included another crown and filling. I was sold at that point. Why not ?\nAlki Dental is very nice, professional, and best of all they take my insurance \"Delta Dental\" Dr Park is a very good dentist  she fit my temporary crowns perfectly which was a relief compared to my last dentist. The staff is professional and explained everything about the process. I didn't give a 5 star, because I am a new patient and not completed with my crown process. But so far so good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gus Marks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS46BGTa7q5KGiEwTPbp0F8TgCc2Y6k7TyGZ5UTAkovV4uqrtC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am TERRIFIED of the dentist, but I love it here!! This is the first dentist I've ever gone to where they make sure my mouth is actually numbed before drilling!! Everyone is so incredibly nice and it makes me feel so much more at ease!! Also, I dont have insurance, but using their membership and payment plans options make it waaaaaay more accessible!! There's some street parking and also a paid lot within walking distance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE9iZ7XQ5Wcdi4RrNmjwsXNl0M1PEkY-Xts8Gs6D_lAfAc6vViqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for the first time yesterday! First off the location is great if you want a view of the beach while you get your mouth worked on! Doesn’t hurt to have a nice view! Secondly, the staff were all great! From the front desk being super friendly and helpful to the DA being kind and very reassuring. The dentist themselves also was great, I had recommendations from her that were necessary and not from a viewpoint of wanting to sell another service. She also prevented me from having to unnecessarily do a procedure that in the past other dentists have been eager to get me to “fix”. I felt welcomed, heard, and assured. Highly recommend coming here!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn03BVNI7RN1Mh388gEalPzkNfRfyANqNRI1lDb7MF3g_ydJ9UcScVpOzc0euHpb7qRwjAhhSHG7vXR2dAtaQlPOhO0WksUsRNaQnfCwMWss1mR2tZUPZJ6KIphnlRo3L8XTLPdA=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Michael Giulietti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_JCog0BKlgm70aEMgNg-QQgtjjyuKY47UeuEnVK8aq2Q6deLn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'd say their strength is doing what you ask. For example, their cleanings were too gentle so I asked them to go rougher. Now I leave spitting blood every time! Cons would be that the dental chairs are pretty worn out and everything has a yellow tinge to it. I can overlook this though. They have some of the best x-ray technology I've seen, are nice, have a clean facility, parking's pretty good... I've gone three times and plan to keep going back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ronald Lohse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSrwlHJLOWuo4knsham24rDWzy7vUS29jcCm4UhwlkQPfbGyQx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alki Dental has taken care of all of my dental needs with great service. They accommodate and reschedule when I need to even with short notice. They keep me informed about upcoming procedures and make sure I am comfortable with everything during them. The staff are very friendly and knowledgeable and make my visits a pleasant experience. I have been a patient of Dr. Chi since 2019.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Armstrong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpjRVt4eRrYWwWqHAVsLlimvXHh0jkYfNmWIhIu5UEpXjzq_2r=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the team at Alki Dental. They’re professional, on time, thorough and provide excellent customer service. I value supporting local business in West Seattle and this is one I highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theron Page","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpMvVOM2WzFf4LzOzUEgLKLWHaheL-8MYtySumhw1lXJRqNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Park and the team at Alki Dental were great. I don’t really like going to the dentist but the whole team made it an overall great experience. They even liked my dog (Bailey). Thanks to all at Alki Dental.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn21KqZhDs7pu_xk_EGAOEoggeIimFiZcHrL26v_5Oc8TA6FDRN2MrWzsj89EUZvT_ZDg-OUH0AfPW4D2VlxAtCFXX7zBg0OvG_yX9w99L6-Ya_7UwkIkYkZGjyyYyIO-XNM8mJn=k-no"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Joo Coo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQpqyKjY9WM_vvFZDXFSu62t0fYLOSkcAodJnY8ZwoF2l1Lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Alki Dental in West Seattle. The office is beautiful, modern, and equipped with some of the latest dental technology. Dr. Ko took excellent care of my dental needs, making the process of getting fillings and a night guard seamless and comfortable.\n\nOne of the things I appreciate most about this office is the calm and welcoming atmosphere—there’s never a sense of being rushed, and parking is always convenient. The entire staff is friendly, professional, and attentive, making each visit a pleasant one.\n\nHighly recommend Alki Dental for anyone looking for top-quality dental care in an stress-free environment!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1CgSWxud260YZP-dX_tFuD2hhb0ilvCStDSC46JgUnup13QMMpCsV6VlUp4-hiUSn5R5i-ft9foDjMmk71qTu67_y_oe4zlL90xk3cYFFxoCbvzVAsLXeMiSSgASmZe4FeBa-rgQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-2"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
