injyuoLz8gkrgR2VnHEs9mDeF7z83--aebWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at North Seattle Smile today for a routine cleaning and check-up. The front desk staff was welcoming and very organized, which made the check-in process a breeze. Dr. Nguyen was incredibly professional and took the time to walk me through my X-rays in a way I could actually understand. I usually find dental visits a bit stressful, but I felt completely at ease here. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roberta Nolan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJo4P_9kPjnprTg7S9P3wpibQYQd5SS26l4LUOmS-NSCv2ZXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For whatever reason, I wasn't feeling my previous dentist so I just didn't go regularly but I do know the importance of keeping up dental care.  I got a recommendation to see Dr. Nguyen from a friend who has been a long time client.  The location is very easy and has free parking available which is a great plus.  I met the staff and all were very upbeat, warm and friendly.  Finally, I found Dr. Nguyen and staff to be equally as friendly, knowledgeable and thorough.  They have current equipmentI got all my questions answered.\n\nFor my first visit I had an excellent experience and am so glad to lock down a long term dental provider that is in my network.  I've already booked my next follow ups into the future and am recommending their office to my family and friends!  Finally, I'm excited to catch up on my dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYqs8FInrW6P23qAv4mAi6CZSmGuVz1ItOgjWH1L5ZI1rABQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to make a switch to a new dentist after I moved to North Seattle - this was hard for me as I LOVED my previous dentist downtown. Dr. Nguyen made it easy to be happy with my decison. Dr. Nguyen has great bedside manner and in comparison to other dentists, he was more hands-on than any other dentist I have gone to in my life. I appreciate his time to sit down; show me my XR; and educate me on what they were showing him. The hygienist and front office staff are personable and efficient, as well. 10/10.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kay Hurd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkXaG5YVvTuNVKj3m6FucY1XGLUKkSJvjUoNz5yXDp6gUGwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm so fortunate to have such a caring, knowledgeable and educated dentist.  His staff is an extension of his excellence. He is gentle, and available for regular and emergencies.  Another plus+, Doctor N employs top dental hygienist(s).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIL8eJpDqG4P-KW0cABVyR3SbDzG1d-SdWG6sDUBFDioke8Xg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scheduling is easy. Wait times are minimal. There is plenty of free parking. The clinic is clean and all of the staff members were very nice and professional. They did a great job with my teeth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5e2usLm8O6Wt-SXLPIHaUk9P7hwWnRDEMpx8GiLP2tk3MZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I think all of the staff at North Seattle Smiles is awesome, Claudine is an exceptional Dental Hygienist, explains everything thoroughly and really does a great job. Highly recommend. She  never gives up patiently telling me why I should floss more which I appreciate. 😬","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ken Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWflAsHKuUnbZK6XOqb0zlEZEGrcyY7sFKc8iiMkm71Wom54EqK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff and great dentist who takes the time to answer questions and follow up on things. I’ve been looking for a good office after several subpar experiences in the past and finally found one I love!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barsha Emdad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_x_eQcCWKXXSJ9mj-yZbbyta0t5eLol5tuJ4La9O6irYkpSW4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming to this dental office since I was in middle school, and now I’m in my late 20s. My whole family are patients here too, and we’ve always had a great experience.\n\nClaudine is always my go-to dental hygienist, she is so kind and easy to talk to—and she makes visits really comfortable. She’s quite literally seen me grow up!\n\nDr. Julian Nguyen is thorough and thoughtful, and always takes the time to explain things clearly. Sarah at the front desk is super helpful and friendly—she always makes checking in, scheduling, and insurance arrangements simple.\n\nThere’s a warm, family feel to the place. You can tell they care about their patients and want to help. We’ve been coming here for years, and it’s always been consistent and reliable care.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
