cture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbXEEdmaW3ST-xS-RsaO8KE5eO152g3Ko8J2lc-hSGavmoNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist practice ever. The entire team is so kind and knowledgeable. I always leave feeling so clean. They always answer all my questions thoroughly. Special shoutouts to my dental hygienist Danny who goes the extra mile by providing data-backed education on how to improve my at home routine and suggests effective affordable tools.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roman Schuch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHYjYulZz5wAgKlZ3SBarGnDP59c3_ds5N427pkOgf53oleMLuhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The front desk, hygienist, and doctor were all lovely and professional. They met me where I was and discussed with me what my options would look like for a custom night guard and possible orthodontic care in the future. They have payment plans for out-of-pocket care and can work with you. I really felt comfortable here today.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Becky Tilles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnP8DxCgWbADpis9xVzNOVN5auEC_8CUU1PX5MlE9404tt6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I followed Dr Laura Sauvage from another location and I’m so glad I did. I just had my first cleaning here and. Gisela is fantastic. Dr Laura answered all my questions and Lisa the front desk person went absolutely beyond the call of duty to help me with a logistical problem. I can’t say enough about how great this dental office is!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjOhV8hjvQDK7UqmFPsX_l5SwBTPsmMEppACLmE3fkCCjvituN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best dental care i’ve ever experienced! Everyone there is delightful. They have such a welcoming and fun environment. Dr. Laura Sauvage was helpful, kind, and very knowledgeable. I felt like i had a thousand questions and she seemed excited to answer each one. If you’re looking for a dentist, I HIGHLY recommend this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayla Whited","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhvaw5X8UeWGw_Unk6P0W9IrqT270LeHFp-9ulqfscskDqCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best experience I’ve had at a dentist’s office in a long time! Lisa makes scheduling a breeze, and the hygienists are amazing at making a generally uncomfortable experience a comfortable and relaxed one. Every staff member I’ve encountered has been personable and welcoming, and has been able to answer any questions I have.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kara May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwQ2jm7TKHBSjRWofrD6u7UD1WyNS8Oa9h0rHnxknN-B8Bjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have been going here for years and always a great experience. Hygienists are friendly, efficient, and informative. Always give advice on improving dental health for your specific needs. Dentists are great too. And Lisa at the front desk is amazing! Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Devin Wolf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbXhgRFciMGFNd5xbxK72b98kysQUinwXnIZ_ZYTX9KaoTyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I've been going to this office for 3 years now, and always had a decent experience until my most recent visit. I originally went in for a deep cleaning after not going to the dentist for over a decade. Since then, I've been scheduled for exams and routine cleanings every 4 months (3 times a year). My second to last visit, they examined my pits and they came back better than ever. The dental assistant and doctor both said my teeth were very nice and healthy besides a cavity I had on my very back tooth which they filled. This last visit (4 months later!), complete opposite results from pit examination. The assistant claimed some were deeper than when I had originally went in the very first time, that I had inflammation, and that I need a deep clean again. The doctor assigned to me that day said the same thing. They both asked if I had any changes in brushing and flossing habits which I didn't, or if I smoke, which I don't. I brush and floss twice a day. I asked the doctor why the results this time were so drastically different than the previous visit. All he could tell me was that it was probably a \"misread\". I told them I wasn't going to pay for a deep cleaning right now as it costs hundreds of dollars even with insurance. Mind you, every visit I've had at the place they've given me different people to look at my teeth every single time. It's insane to me that these people can see me 3 times a year and be so off the mark with tracking my progress. What's the point of me going this many times a year if they're going to have different people say different things to me about my dental health every time I visit? I am pretty angry that this even happened. I would give them a 1 star, but I do commend the employees who have been kind and seemingly well meaning in the past. Otherwise, this place is trash. Gonna be looking for another office that has actual consistency.\n\nEdit: knocked down to 1 star, they need to know that this is unacceptable to me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leena Leena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJubA8xNzdZ5CCDnSpX6p1-U2Lh-6uPT12z9lnMYgIPubPxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Paul Sauvage has been an amazing dentist. He’s always quick to help during emergencies, especially when my wisdom tooth pain acts up. I’ve followed him to every clinic. He provides exceptional care — highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
