nts. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tommy Pheap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQ8mgGZi2FyTpwyU4_nWrKWx5Vsk_6Y5eOHBTBAWb_AqdSMuYS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at this dental office. The dentist was very gentle and professional. She cleaned my teeth thoroughly and did a touch-up with great care. I felt comfortable the entire time, and everything was explained clearly. I’m very happy with the results and would definitely recommend her to others.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Mavica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCBpbQUjIUelN7sVRxUjMEo_R_dP0VNIYecxDQUpeZBICEkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough good things about Omni Dental. From the front desk to the clinical team, everyone is consistently kind, caring, and incredibly attentive. They truly take the time to listen, explain things clearly, and make you feel comfortable at every visit. Dental appointments can be stressful, but Omni Dental always makes the experience feel calm and supportive. I feel so fortunate to have found them and to trust them as my dentist. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a compassionate and professional dental team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mary bennett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaescWcVMhO3oXGc_OA20dG-ecave2CZkdM-VREbE6N99pN7o2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've had very positive experiences at Omni Dental, with Dr Hays. She is a good dentist, with a gentle touch, and I received good treatment. I would recommend her as a dentist.\nThe staff is competent and friendly.\nThe office is clean and we'll maintained.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"FaLana Ruffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUragg_ZFcFXXDHoDxFG772gVuhdGhqFeKlRK6yVoZsa2UUc08BuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For those of you looking for a wonderful dentist to go to, Omni Dental is a great start. I came to the dentist with a list of things to do and they handled it all with grace and efficiency! I needed a pediatric referral for my daughters and the team were welcoming and sweet with my toddlers. I haven't been to the dentist in several years and my experience was so smooth and informative. Brittany was gentle and patient when taking x-rays and scans; her polishing skills were just as amazing. I had a lot of photos to do and she got down to business and checked in regularly during the process for my comfort. Andre! My new fave dental hygienist 😁 He did a lovely job of cleaning my teeth and clearing some problem spots I shared with him. Efficient and a lovely chat to ease my nerves made my experience that much better. Dr. Hayes was a GEM! She gave me straightforward information and explained the photos and scans perfectly.  Misty, thank you so much for being able to flex my appointments so I was able to tackle these appointments before going back to work. Front desk area was clean and welcoming as well. I'm personally looking forward to my next appointment even though it's for a few fillings, that should tell you enough! 😉","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_amO9vo-LU-RHeskpQh7RqN27eZ8m5VoQvKbjw5R_ruMc35fiKSKyKxz17jJx0VKrZST9yhWXC2D0ehj_XIdlvebXFyaYD3guOg7l3W8gtLKA67LIfAzfiY7CsPAuxi1W49b88aDHk29Z=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-22"},{"Name":"ezra smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw4nHZrd_nmD9ga1HeNCMFrroE_6GYA_BtYkE1D6yJIp31IxovOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a very stressful day, the omni staff made it all go away. I have never EVER. been treated so well in a medical let alone dental setting. They are truly the best of the best. Dr. Jack and RDH Jenni and Misty are seriously the best kinds of people. Everyone is so accommodating and makes sure that you feel safe and supported. Definitely my primary now","Images":null,"When":""},{"