are! I had an appointment with Tashona today, and she was absolutely amazing—so professional, gentle, and genuinely one of the friendliest people I’ve ever met. I think I want to be her new BFF. 😆 The whole office had a great vibe, and everyone was super welcoming. If you're looking for a dentist where you actually enjoy your visit (yes, really), this is the place. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sabrina Pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8aNutLjW4KOFmNOGmxtMMlgAvmfHwiue9lTr1aLv47CpwHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of seeing KAREN WANG and I can confidently say she is one of the best dentists I’ve ever had. From the moment I walked in, she made me feel completely at ease with her gentle demeanor and kind approach. She took the time to explain everything clearly, which helped ease any anxiety I had. Not only is she efficient, but her skill with her hands is impressive – the procedure I had done was smooth, quick, and completely pain free. I left the office feeling confident and well-cared for. Highly recommend her for anyone looking for a compassionate and skilled dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rodrigo Mendoza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgBBZi-06TtA5adWDOnne0RQBdIoA02w2JZhP9j-EGqk_8rysg3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've only had my initial consultation but it was great! The staff was friendly, human and competent, and they used modern equipment. I tend to be sceptical about dentists recommending too much work but the dentist was clear about the issues I need work on","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Antonio Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVERMFLNZipoHRiJSPeK9R_FO5Sue-nCVsxNdDtPMmgk4yw5Us9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Innovative Denistry is amazing! Angi and Sorigiah at the front desk are amazing, super helpful with setting up and rescheduling my appointments as needed. They both answered all my questions when scheduling. Sorigiah presented the cost before each visit which helped with my dental anxiety immensely.\n\nDental assistant JC was the best! He happily answered all my questions and helped me feel comfortable. Hygienists Jen and Tashona were incredibly accommodating, patient with me and very thorough with cleanings. I would love to see both of them again for cleanings in the future!\n\nDr. Sharma was an absolute pleasure to see. Her treatment plan helped me so much! She never once made me feel ashamed for letting my dental hygiene slip for so long. She was encouraging and I'm excited to come back. I can tell she genuinely cares for her patients. I had an extremely positive experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yulia Ordaz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKie90kbUrZCJoYXntC7HD6IN4nj4z54QSDvn2W_POEp6beKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a patient at this practice for about 7 years, and I couldn’t be happier! They always take great care of me and make every visit a positive experience. I am a patient of Dr. Sharma, she’s kind, professional, and truly attentive. I highly recommend Dr. Sharma and Innovative Dentistry to anyone looking for excellent dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlR0J_6q2WgzbZwAq1JdbPYNVv0ChW0dep1j5t8AGP7HdCHX6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Innovative Dentistry is the best! They provide a warm, welcoming environment with exceptional care. Casey is my hygienist, and she is incredibly knowledgeable, kind, and makes going to the dentist such a positive experience!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
