inue to bring my family to her and recommend others to her. (She was highly recommended by several of my co-workers at my former clinic).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mellisa Kapp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs_SnFPI0JZ1ASMFnhL9pX05dm-5zCmQ41v66I14rkb8Owr3wS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I feel so lucky to have found Dr Dehkordi!  She is so patient, thorough and extremely knowledgeable.   My son actually referred me to her and now I literally recommend all my friends and family to 5th ave Dentistry.\nThank you Dr Dehkordi!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKRaOgsOzTEWLI8tNkTfvJxd1Ruo5c3yzhSi2DvUo7YfooTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Dehkordi is an awesome Dr. with great personality very respectful and kind I have been going here since 2006 , she is never deman nor pushy, she focuses on her work so much she makes you feel like you are very important person. she would give you an opportunity to think and decide, if she sees something needs to be done. I like her So much I would recommend to anyone who needs a Very Good dentist to go any try her.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lyn Coffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsDeqzcDb5u5ZMfu5VOf5dbb4ERfg2iCPvf4p62X4UgziyTc0c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Dehkordi has been my dentist for 15 years. She is fantastic. I'm almost happy to go to the dentist. She's respectful and very skilled.  I have No reservations or complaints.  A plus!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lis Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQS_z8dCvC9gFkdtzGQNZe__ujQ_YcoM_IJUIeg019Mxio5LZH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a very good place to go for teeth care. Dr Dehkordi is a very competent dentist. I recommend her highly. She's really nice too. She was the first dentist to make a care plan for me so