Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Bailey Hosking","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJi6xH3GrHj7f2zA6Xn23Ki8ZZGYgZxB2xN2aR1swhhu8XtKXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I could not be more impressed with Dr. Goel and the Pure Dental Arts team. My entire experience was seemless. Dr. Goel skipped all of the nonsense i have experienced with far too many dentists in the past; no attempts to upsell or  recommend expensive unsolicited procedures. He quickly addressed my concern and sent me on my way. I wish I had found them years ago.\n\nAfter literal years of delaying intervention, bouncing from dentist to dentist, and things deteriorating to where I was in so much pain I couldnt sleep at night, I finally booked a new patient emergency appointment online after hours. Fortunately they were able to see me the following morning. Both the online booking and receptionist informed me that the initial visit was a consultation, and any work might have to be scheduled out - completely reasonable. Much to my surprise, after a quick consult Dr. Goel asked if I wanted to do the procedure today, warning i might \"be in the chair a while\". A couple minutes later I was being presented reasonable, transparent pricing. A total of 50 minutes elapsed from when i walked in the door, to when i walked out. During that time I was treated with kindness and dignity.\nI absolutely recommend Dr. Goel, especially to anyone who has had past negative experiences from predatory dentists like I have.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna Farrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO-f-FjKsE1qg1I1qpV-TTEmYdUHx5lJYThkv2OisxLKgtNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Felt rushed. Poor bedside manner. Doctor told me I need a crown within minutes, then tried to schedule the appointment and not do the cleaning that day, when that was part of the reason why I was there. Felt pressured to make the decision about the crown to also get the cleaning my teeth needed, especially since it had been a while since my last cleaning. I insisted on getting the cleaning that day, since that's what I was there for, and the hygienist was very rushed, rough, and didn't do a careful job, I could still feel plaque in areas he didn't get very well due to the rushing. I ended up going to another dentist to get a second opinion about the crown and was told I didn't need one yet. There seems to be a lot of good reviews for this place, so you experience may be better, but I just didn't feel at ease during my appointment or like I could trust their recommendations. Also the 3D imaging of my teeth felt hacky and completely unnecessary. I don't care if you can make a 3d image, I care if my dentist can provide gentle trustworthy care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Riley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBZeB25oA9w2PxxG3uw-Ev2753ORgZD-01gDcNTYf817gwB_c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience overall! My insurance changed after the new year and I’m so happy I chose Pure Dental Arts as my new dentist. Very clean, welcoming, and professional.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kylie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI21L_pmXGXpEu3mZabQkwkVqfMAxeSCQBbxR1QufELFNv1sIaPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to this office for 2 years and every visit has been seamless. I’ve never had to wait more than 3 minutes to be seen by the hygienist and the appointments are efficient. The whole staff is friendly and professional, office is always clean. It does get super quiet in the office, maybe they could play some music or use the TVs but not a huge deal. Great neighborhood dentist! Please don’t get bought out by a PE firm🙏","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"pratik bhangale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrThWkWfdlILcbPVGyP3uBKBrO_xoq6fkMiFbtgVo0KIrn-nLc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming here for 5 years. Extremely well maintained and accurate treatment of every tooth related issues.\nBoth Dr. Chiang and Dr. Goel are so good. Most important all the staff is really kind and gives you good experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lizelle Salanga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLLXwiW_ovkRlPh9wSXD3tlI-YERN7THThU_Q71Teo9VnWeBY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ivan, Joselin, and Dr. Chiang were all so lovely and efficient. All questions were answered with patience. I'll be back for my follow-up visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ian Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-OoKzilfUi2qdgl1B8idvX5ae-PBbX9TAaZKqQ74KOaLiarJOwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve gone here 3 times for cleanings over the past year and a half and it’s always been a great experience. Everyone is friendly and thorough with their work. I always seem to be done either early or on time, which is a big plus.\n\nHappy to keep coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mathangi t","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmPhi6gI8GhW51d_OjNv6PGem41xIzIk0j-mp8YOaKHNZ7BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent dental clinic with very caring doctors and staff. Felt comfortable throughout.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
