tent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1U9-mEj0ZD-_JnCKlPfoIrJIBQXzlnp6kHTzd_ld78CQDZTo8hRAvnV5X6IrBLuHAp0Pqm4fHXjACSSBWld-8vP_j-mUBRBzjDnf-nL__bjsyOFD3RwwjNNQkXcgqHq1a32CFcsA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2m6mId2Fkk2EUUixQ5IKHw-5avA-bEhWlX3Gmnw3qo8Mcm0_FaJABA1I6pD8QeXRiMoQ7T7L6K1eTMVteuAdaTMbUo74wJ7v6VzuIjpDzxI4Ni0A-dukU7LYSPv0H-7l8h8_aQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3rCqAc1tRxJsJ_F_7QEJAG0pISO0FrmQxKtmwA9263dy9K7wwQ3L9zkcEzbJ7NPKf93L2E0rtFLFzDYvOGaQxXyO7RmKUtaoayo87KgCyxZlRAl9Enrv-DYnkPmG-XE-E72N096w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3nmUf3HgL8jhZJOtcNyk4JXF8FyIMvpnP6DBxnoMazcTJ0Np7m-ifnYdARRexiZWq6SzWyOexVD4G2lWAklRYQgCMmBfW7qrbbyLeEQxKb1njBrYG0ZEHS9E8hOZCoRyMrza8-=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2y3Mg9ug1q2b2Ur_c8S7FxJtM2Hj8X-3Vmvvk0uk4gQ-SiFyF5rTjKoRUWIOErTSS-dRGSyVErbojVQu0Z52YI-1e-CKjcDvnqF5ZmwBbu2u6sA5CPJdM20HEaXB7WyQFSDAl8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_ByL8xXocMq7XsOueAFqkBU-3-jQeYBAM9DTswfkfqoQa8BsHx-oVKUKJxFNQTeO_7uCnAV_CUEsrRPzHBOnz_ngZmLdg8QS5sR9uIQqHeJMo-v6VJFxpcF5YPUmrYGt1d2Hd=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-12"},{"Name":"Tonia Bartz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU76mxC93rY1_ZZkd7sNCPV6msDZW6feyJW_RldEP3wY9WAyP9M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a very anxious dental patient, and even the easiest cleaning or set of x-rays can be too much. Dr. Park and her team at Fremont Dental are extremely patient and understanding on top of being knowledgable. I have always felt able to express my concerns, anxiety or questions to them without feeling less than, and they do their best to make sure that I am comfortable (as comfortable as you can truly be at a dental visit anyway). And if that wasn't enough, the front staff is wonderful, and I can always email if I have a question, rather than needing to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaitie Ivory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1HQlzAyffx4Y_9PsG9cKxwzUpQ9TyZJq2687d51x9XpXbIw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had a really positive experience with my dentist overall over the last several years. The office is welcoming, the staff is gentle, and the treatments were thorough. I particularly loved being able to watch TV during my fillings—it really helped calm my anxiety and made the whole process much more comfortable.\n\nThat said, the scheduling was a bit of a challenge. I called two months in advance to reschedule my appointment, and they told me the next available slot was six months out. They encouraged me to call back in May, so I did, but they still didn’t have openings and suggested I call back weekly until something became available. Unfortunately, I just didn’t have the time to keep calling, so I ended up making an appointment with another dentist who could see me sooner, but I'll miss them.\n\nOverall, great care once I was able to get in, but the scheduling process was frustrating and could use some improvement. I’d still recommend them for their excellent service and calming atmosphere if you’re able to book an appointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"laura s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1iyUYmv1bD8nfF4luyEu1MrAKuAR2qxlcxo-ABF62cNevZy4u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Park has been my dentist for over ten years! The level of attention to detail and care provided is excellent. Also gotta give a shout out to the awesome hygienists! Chelsea is so wonderful and does such a thorough job and even manages to remember the small talk we had during my last appointment 6 months previous! Front desk ladies are amazing as well. The entire staff provides such great care that I would definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Balbas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViHLhWF7dCr2cFXvGlSQLUdGpsJ6A1NPehKfcVbPZu0gUNrB1D=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Lisa Park and her talented team continue to rise above my expectations. Dr Park is one of the most patient and skilled dentists I have found! She took on a very difficult bridge, saving my smile. They work with me to make sure I can afford the procedures by assessing, then creating a plan that maximizes insurance over time. Their professionalism, attention to every detail, transparency, kindness and skill keep me a loyal and very satisfied patient. I moved out of the area last year but drive back in to Fremont for my dental care because they are the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Mansfield","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo0KfHu7fP_XZZZTqLRqJPpGIdt4Dgfp9BmnLYgO90fNVfSPtH_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I have been treated by Dr. Kim for the last 8 years and highly recommend her and her hygienists. We’ve been treated with minor fillings, referrals for a gum graft and long overdue root canal, replacement retainers, tooth whitening, and maintenance for a dental implant. Dr. Kim is empathetic, detail oriented, and does dental procedures well and aesthetically— my crown perfectly matches my other teeth! Everyone is friendly and efficient, making going to the dentist anxiety free.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cintia Luna-Villasana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6u1-nKe4hIXeYEZ2j2M4_nAMqyv4XAFS1P02HcY19CslEGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Fremont Dental! I went to Fremont Dental when I felt like my teeth had hit the point of no return - or so I thought. After years of neglecting my teeth, I had tooth decay and many other issues. I was embarrassed! However the kindness and care of the team is amazing, they didn't make me feel bad or judged. The team fixed my dental issues and gave me tips on how to maintain good dental hygiene. I cannot thank this dental office enough, Dr. Park and everyone there for there awesome work. I always look forward to my checkups now, and am happy to have my smile back.\n\nAlso, the prices for dental work is amazing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liliana Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_9tsOdwYOboPFsjlkPc3BRUNsigg1Es-gagOqP3vcsD2YHuY-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Fremont Dental. I came to them almost six years ago for emergent pain. They fit me in quickly and figured out what I needed. Since then, they accommodate my schedule easily, fit me in quickly for any emergencies, and referred me to the best endodontist. Dr. Kim is non judgmental, takes time to answer my questions, and prepares me honestly. The office staff are so lovely too. I’m a nurse, and I trust them completely.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
