","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Starla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkXK5-wNaqiO7dYgH-0hb2GhIuWrzQchkke9DDh4D8icojzdMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed to see a dentist asap and Belltown Modern Dentistry was able to fit me in the next morning. It was my first time going here and I was a little nervous due to past experiences of dental offices pushing aggressive treatment plans that were costly and not really necessary. The girl at the front desk, Linda, assured me that this wouldn't be the case here and that costs would be discussed with me prior to any treatments being done. She was right! The dentist, Andy Hsu, was super nice and very thorough. He recommended a medication called Curodont to treat a few baby cavities that I had but said it was completely up to me if I wanted to just monitor them instead. I was really comfortable and the pricing was more reasonable than I expected so I decided to get the treatment and am really excited about it. I was even was able to buy the Opalescence teeth whitening trays that I see everyone on TikTok rave about! Feels so much nicer to buy them from an actual dental office than from Amazon. Will definitely be back to visit this office again!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0y5V5nyHjvMItneajwgE6hUPxP_eMxZOvUFkiClUMUuaoYq2afIs-wG55OiRHKnWumTzkkCjyXTXWn2CbRS2AKLtyjm_BRMjp_RNdGQOEpsUpvLHAtQ0GA2Hc5wv79kmGYXxyASPD9QDY=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-4"},{"Name":"Alicia Potts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmiWcVek9DJu3fZjWiR3rzXOkz7RGBoJ1-2bcR2JxOzrz4kRxa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently moved here from Southern California and have been searching for a new dentist, so I’m really grateful I found Belltown Modern Dentistry. I accidentally took the wrong exit on the way to my appointment and ended up running a few minutes late, but when I called to let them know, they were incredibly kind and understanding, which immediately put me at ease.\n\nThe entire team was friendly and welcoming. Carol, the dental hygienist, was so knowledgeable and clearly passionate about her work. Dr. Reimer was also excellent, she explained each step along the way and made sure I understood everything that was happening.\n\nI received a cleaning for $59 and added a fluoride varnish for $25, bringing the total to $84. I’ve definitely paid much more at other places and didn’t feel the cleanings were nearly as thorough as they were here. Thank you to the team at Belltown Modern Dentistry. I’m looking forward to my next visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dorothy Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7X5oPn7BV3jK31xrIvcbQ19u4ZCQY8Xd-5TUDm0yT8EGlbNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's been years since I've last gone to the dentist, primarily out of sheer laziness. So, I chose Belltown Modern Dentistry based on my colleague's recommendations as well as its convenient and safe location. Man let me tell you - this was the BESTTTT dentist experience I've ever had in my entire life with Dr. Andy Hsu \u0026 his assistance Elizabeth. They are the funniest people I've ever met in my life yet very knowledgeable and professional in all that they do. They were so so wonderful to be around for the three hours I was in the office. The dentist's office is all about the experience, and these two wonderful people not only created the most amazing environment but made all the procedures nearly pain-free and as comfortable as possible.\n\nThey're extremely transparent on pricing, which was important to me because I'm not a huge fan of hidden fees and charges. They provide an invoice of all the procedures for you to review before starting any operations. I had quite a lot done over the three hours I was there since it had been such a long time for me, but boy I was sad to leave the office because I would not get the Dr. Hsu experience again until 6 months down the line. I will exclusively be going back to this dentist for as long as I live in the greater Seattle area.\n\nHighly highly recommend this place and would give 10/5 stars if I could. Looking forward to my next appointment with Dr. Hsu \u0026 Elizabeth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chloe Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJksx1HiAO62YWEaC7e6Y1rSgO954YX1csq74Vgi6lU8eKgeA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best dental experience here at Belltown modern dentistry. Everyone is super nice and professional. Dr Isabela explained to me my procedures and the reason in detail to make sure I’m comfortable with what’s going to happen. Elisabeth was the most detail oriented assistant I’ve met. She put vaseline on my lips so my lips won’t hurt when opening mouth big. The team was very patient with all my questions and respected my choice when there were options. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elaine Harrison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdQArx9qXhk0s4SzJ62T9U8Kvd8N9gMvPU2OC9eALmN2vnrg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I lost a crown while flossing before bed.  I called, planning to leave a message to be read when the office opened on Monday.  I got a live person who was able to schedule me for an appointment on Monday morning!  The crown was not damaged and there was no decay, so it was reseated and I was on my way with a permanent fix.  I am very pleased with the care I received.  I was able to leave for vacation as planned!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"George Jingyuan Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6zF2y-yVI-FgBmGXwYT6rLvmq9eJ6vic3avVnngcXZ6k3-g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Hsu and Elizabeth are absolutely amazing! This was my first visit, and they provided a complimentary check-up before proceeding with the cleaning. They were super professional and friendly throughout the entire process. This has truly been the most meticulous cleaning experience I've ever had. I would highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SoCal 4K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCr1pdCqGL9Rcey7e3GYEM0kjUELp1M6j4Ud7lVeOaGN8sCc4ycA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dental experience ever w Dr Hsu and Elizabeth! They were so meticulous and thorough it’s unmatched by any other dental work done prior. I highly recommend everyone to give their service a shot!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgE95xX-HqcoTrM-9hNZJBsBW6qcGbO4BnRhQLoV2870KnlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst experience ever. Really should not risk my teeth there.\n\nI came there to have a regular exam and clearning. I was told I got some caries. After the dentist (Tzu-Chien Hsu) did the filling for the first two, both teeth have pain for weeks and I cannot eat hard food. The dentist redid the filling, the problems remained. During filling, the assistant talked and laughed, which was very unprofessional.\n\nI had to switch to another place and fix the issues, wasting time and money. Really should read the bad reviews before I came there.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
