tch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102226026465034669469","name":"Biederman Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102226026465034669469"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Green Lake","street":"7900 East Green Lake Dr N #300","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98103","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Gr25","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOF5ahlIaAoKMWohZFxHDJ92MWRYgshyDLzVWS2hDxvAz4hR4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Biederman and his team go out of their way to make their patients feel comfortable, taken care of and prioritized. As someone who has experience life long dental anxiety, I have never felt more comfortable at a dentist’s office. I broke a filling over the weekend and it fell out leading to sensitivity. Dr.Biederman and his team were able to schedule me to the first possible appointment open and then worked to immediately fix my tooth that very day. They made a 24 week pregnant, very anxious patient feel so much better and took excellent care of me. My hygienist went above and beyond to comfort me and explain everything they were doing and kept me distracted which made the appointment fly by. They were so reassuring about modifying the treatment to make sure it was safe for me and the baby. I am incredibly grateful for them and could not recommend them more.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melinda Denson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIz1r-wlvAYXqSpi_n5PXhSx6ml-F6esA_gNS1I-gfChCJhcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very positive experience.  Dental cleaning and evaluation of home care since the last appointment. No new issues observed.  Questions answered about toothpaste product that helped to limit plaque deposits.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Simsons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsp60NLwhp2h1382_iw1MMqduF39gd07cIxs4pUAQ8kGYMGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's always nice to review when there were no cavities. Dr. Biederman did a short consult on my teeth. The star of the show was the hygienist! I learned some things from her. It's hard to talk to these people with you mouth open; but she was careful and smart and thoughtful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"rosie reid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHvHzGSC4c_uMzGqgxTlyDJOp2pVt4lKQEs1Nm-GBrKsfgeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been happy with this clinic for years fit my regular dental needs and have just returned from receiving periodontal cleanings elsewhere. I’m thrilled to be back under the gentle, patient, and expert care of Dr. Biederman and his staff, with a special shout out today to Lacy and Terra!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWipxYgd4FyjknBYWG5dp1mOos7b06yarmFHtMUAzqcf3n1wxo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Emily did a fantastic job during my appointment both in teeth cleaning and information regarding preventative care. And Dr. Biederman has always been efficient and great during checkups.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine Trout","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbTXYyCV4M1yPH25uiAP8pQk-qVm_MYrEdY-qu832JLFKeXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really can’t express how grateful I am for Dr. Biederman and his staff! They went above and beyond with my dental care, and were consistently compassionate, empathetic, and kind. I had an oral implant on one of my front teeth and needed a crown to replace the previous tooth - as a young woman in her 20s with a history of complex teeth/connective tissue issues, I had a lot of anxiety around the tooth/gum blending in with the other teeth and looking better instead of worse than before. Dr. Biederman navigated all these complications with such grace and professionalism, and pursued numerous custom paths to get to the best result possible. Thank you, Biederman Dentistry!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Pickens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKgvFTYX6qDX6zDjuvzdubwZYwmdeYqBrPhIhvOZYKQdkgdh0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lindsay is the best dental hygienist I have ever worked with.  Mariam at the front desk is terrific and really knows me and my family.  Very efficient practice with good communication.  Dr. Biederman is always so kind and thorough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Wittenberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUAbGGoLjF7Qi4lTsEzA-lKxfMhsO6rygDbRNafFER-ZlMQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Professional, welcoming and efficient office! Everyone was engaging, helpful and good at their job. I will be recommending this office to friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
