e was such a breath  of fresh air. So helpful and answered all the questions I had. She was such a gem she made this whole experience so much easier to navigate through as im not particularly fond of dentist visits, but she went above and beyond to make me feel at ease. 10/10 for this office. Great work, amazing staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJlOS_qoaQcz8MB8l87jZdWEBUOFrEdrCfBU1UQWtcPkCQZICNTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Northgate Smiles. Like so many other reviewers have said, everyone in the office is so kind and warm- especially Heidi, who was my hygienist. She took the time to explain various things I can do at home for better gum health, and made the overall appointment stress-free. I highly recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tk Premium sneaker reviews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1We1eDmpYaxBq2nhnlgSNjuVroGBR00EJKkCVqu0d9ymzDZV9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a wonderful experience at Northgate Smiles! From the moment I walked in, Cassie at the front desk made me feel so welcome and comfortable she’s friendly, professional, and always has a warm smile. Dr. Lu was amazing thorough, gentle, and really took the time to explain everything and make sure I was comfortable throughout my visit. The whole team works so well together and you can tell they truly care about their patients. I highly recommend Northgate Smiles to anyone looking for a great dental office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ginger Chaffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9OhgKCRbWu7jtsGpjTb_LDoq-s-FbQB9FD-dgli76NrNbI4tS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great team of skilled a caring professionals. They were attentive to my needs and made me feel at ease. I have been very pleased with the dental work I've received for several years now. I highly recommend Northgate Smiles.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
