atient here for years, and I cannot recommend them highly enough. The entire staff is incredibly personable, and the treatments are thorough and done with great care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Trey Littell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxu9UH5g9EFvEsVMkFKN31Z2S9fs4tauwVprY7JxVrIBN_WIWcAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a 5 star dentist. Do your teeth a favor. Go to this dentist! They are knowledgeable, experienced, talented, and passionate about your teeth. They did everything for way less than other dentists quoted me. Their customer service, capabilities, and overall treatment of their customers is world class. I have never gotten such pain free cost effective work done anywhere. This dental practice has such a wonderful team. I couldn’t be happier, and my teeth couldn’t look better. If this isn’t your first choice for dental work in Seattle, you are risking it. Go here and be confident that you will be treated right and not get overcharged.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KGOqeEkylOJ3HkHs0SxNA3bWfcUaOALEDnsm0ZNDQZVsM8OkMkk1yDy3HdSXtXwXv-4Qb8wG8-1S0wt68f2nHXEDCZnyk5VW6TyMNEv2JCXSFiGap-vJXxUCe3zsi0LtbdozLaQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3MmJeYwt2LGP3AlfZVUk_vXCa-PfS0-OXA1cft5gEtPlI2qRqgjlGWmpZpTy2ihQ6mW4Tj9x9Iv_aDsSOZ7snwgNM-ahq7LZEdS0jDFqdBp-Th9fWzKDufgyuuFtM9vP2-k9s=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0QrKl8__WJUX1EnXl09_xpqWxux49WRvTLfPrZVewsZ_pzE8kxdLKAmwZc8bfnkUbAJrxRD7twxkadIhAvIm6PxmOuD0CjSHjKK1w7Oj7TQv8ETgYUlP0R16Y_kSriY2Td1Epv=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn11JW0z76ayV4VcUmTnNpjjdL3VibRLmrqMyM5FGaEo5PBOY1TEliPY0BDwzU2VZ624VzvKOXihKrNzx19iTTkv6U5YqLOo6HFI5PUGzT4OykW11-4M8SALvbgoGZ2vva6V30Vh=k-no"],"When":"2019-5-24"},{"Name":"Scott Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHsPpjU-baqLxn3H0MXFU7XwE2Tp9_alKG9Hu2-9KS-8YzXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Descript