rvations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"109117120101115431340","name":"Woodland Park Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109117120101115431340"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Wallingford","street":"4814 Interlake Ave N","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98103","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Aisha Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDBIWWKdwQTVliNB76aZQ80BffGIs8CfDz5qNJQXQB1zK9k2rN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m so late to leaving my review but I wanted to make sure I took time to do one. I recently moved but I miss coming to this dental office. Best service by Danny!! He’s friendly and kind! He always checks in with me when I visit to see how I was adjusting to Seattle. When you have providers who take time remember you and what’s going on with you it makes a difference. You start to feel more comfortable and welcomed. Also, his staff is always friendly and professional. This office was the best dentist experience I’ve had. I truly Danny and team and sending them my best! If you’re looking for a dentist office don’t hesitate to come here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S Hoover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxSMM3EqGJA7h1AV_uKXjbNZFe6QtlLL9ougZxO7ymuDeKo3n6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had the most wonderful experience with Dr. Danny Lee! Not only is he incredibly skilled and knowledgeable, but he is also very personable and can give you some highlights of Seattle if you’re new to the area. From the moment I walked into the office, I felt welcomed. Dr. Lee took the time to listen to my concerns, thoroughly explain each step of the process, and answer all of my questions. His gentle approach made my dental visit a positive one, and I left feeling confident that I was in good hands for the first time in years. I highly recommend Dr. Lee to anyone in need of a dentist who goes above and beyond in providing exceptional care along with a warm and friendly attitude.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAdsCeOzUtPRmUoM788HzWXzl4R3JxOnC9ik4dVn56HtiJDVTh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lee is great!! He made room in his schedule to accommodate my appointment, greeted me at the door, and was very friendly throughout the visit. He was also incredibly considerate of my dental anxiety, and consistently checked to make sure I was okay and if I had any questions. It almost felt like visiting a friend. His assistant was also very helpful and kind over the phone and in person! Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rae H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZMEXa7R4vN8Op0ylvWELrP0sKpbpR4-ZnwqDsJctxRwRJR84=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really enjoyed the amazing team here at Woodland Park Dental!!! Highly recommended. They are responsive over email if you ever have questions, and every single staff member is really warm and friendly, Dr. Danny Lee especially! I've been seeing them for almost 3 years, like clockwork every 6 months, using various insurances (MetLife \u0026 Guardian Dental). They never recommend anything they don't believe in and always prioritize your care. I live in the neighborhood so it's a quick hop over, but they have plenty of street parking around as well. Sadly have to find a new dentist across the country now that I've moved!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danny Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJp6dzZ3F6GqzpFg2pYaooQ5FDsw74cBcMkxA6r7PA5Zwqa_Zpn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to see Danny at Woodland Park Dental for years now and it is always a great experience. Danny is very personable and always very clear about what's going on with my teeth and what my options are. Since coming here, I really don't really mind dental visits anymore! My only qualm is that I want to chat more but struggle to do so because my mouth is held open :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connor Sauby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyNgFYJGb23DvWkUVMoN9EDUItpJJoRCVrCjoZThv80RUghw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Danny runs a spectacular dentist office. I actually look forward to coming here. Dr. Danny remembers your name and what you are up to. He really breaks the ice and makes you feel at ease. It’s like catching up with a friend.\n\nDr. Danny cares about your teeth immensely and will do what it takes to keep you healthy. Whenever I hear of someone looking for a dentist I recommend woodland park dental. I’ve never liked dentists (who does?), but Dr. Danny is different and I can’t recommend him and Woodland Park Dental enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXgAEMbm3k5Wqg1d9ONdqZRtJig6UI9jKfibnF9IOxIweB5EL7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience here with Dr. Lee and his team. Took the time to explain each procedure to me, and made sure my needs/concerns were all addressed. Looking forward to my next appointment!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tatiana Sreenivasan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZqILwsh3AdZt52bCYceUM0B1qtqVaT-1ovlKXkNswjL86psc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lee is a great dentist! I've asked him various weird questions about oral health and dentistry and he answers them thoroughly and makes sure I'm following his explanations. He also really cares about his patients and would ask me questions about how certain life events went if I mentioned it the last time I saw him. I highly recommend Dr. Lee for all your dentistry needs :).","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
