ollover, etc) \u0026 doesn't pressure you. Good place. I've moved now but I'll be commuting in to cap hill to keep going here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J Alger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAAeecRhqvfTYV8oC5hbNcKewg_apDdvCDKpRAn1Um_bvifA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New to this dentist. He is very good and explains his care and makes a plan to restore.  I’m happy to have found him. Office staff is very pleasant and attentive.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Lindsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjr_NOu3fS7bAz8iLt3G_oz1FyEZKUqyVVCJuQT21CfLQm9KBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Miyata is kind, thorough \u0026 professional. His staff are very pleasant and friendly. I also liked the charming office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D. Cañon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6211KdFxzHBj-pIRWkWt7HNELen3xgXh5eEBd5FivyWxBpXe--A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Zen clinic with my friend and had an outstanding experience! The staff was incredibly welcoming and friendly, making me feel at ease from the moment I walked in. The dental team did an excellent job cleaning my teeth, and I was impressed by their attention to detail.\n\nThe entire process was smooth, efficient, and pain-free. I appreciated the explanations and guidance provided throughout the appointment. The clinic's warm and modern atmosphere only added to the positive experience.\n\nThank you, Zen Dental, for your exceptional service and dedication to dental care. I'm so grateful to have found a trusted dental clinic that truly cares about their patients' well-being. I highly recommend them to anyone seeking top-notch dental care!\n\nRating: 5/5 stars\"","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1HRxZH16zX_fz9fNZ8iSQOt6xS664pCQlPxyQ-ZT5KiKJuA8ZOPBOkXyWzvu0pDo5jn4RBisslESHhsFUGqTmL6CTAW2_E9BmX4uDGFHEGFxvPPbpglE7ekEIQvruObb7sLDuA=k-no"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Jennifer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ599WI59KmyUTtSt8iJtLpy7sa0q3eskKRKDfGH_LJtOI2Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice office. The staff and Dr. Miyata is excellent and honest. Very comfortable and my anxiety is gone.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn01ECL8UQ6x3QdkZYKvZ0XYYP-gOyVxdAlFC3w_OZ1W955RNLVvNrfKWGEZlupCoyWTApsDH7Z8O_Th6PFapszrUXQRbaaWU0vqn6Rp8e2ojqcw1lsZtUZhvevCNqqmsudXdk3RMQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-9"},{"Name":"Kina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqIohzGATPlR_1049r14X6y_IaVHFPvRuyoRpR_zh_LVJNVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Referred by a friend for an emergency appt, called and was brought in same day. Handled that and started coming up with a treatment plan\n\nContinued on to work with them and might i say, they just really care. The doctor (Dr.Miyata) is not one i come across often. And i have not had great luck with prior dentists in the past.\n\nScared due to pain?? Don't be, never felt a pinch or anything.\nWorried about finances? Don't be, talk to them.\nBlubbering away? Dont stress, they are so understanding, kind and patient.\n\nDr.Miyata is meticulous, kind, clearly well trained and educated and truly just fricking cares and that goes so far, esp nowadays.\n\nNow my kids will be transitioning over to this office as well and we will continue.\n\nI feel lucky, really that i was referred to this dentist office","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
